 const messages = JSON.parse("{\"BydgLQ\":\"Education\",\"bQPEog\":\"A minimalist logo for my creative design studio “Borcelle”\",\"3n5EFw\":\"Undo\",\"PZPxRw\":\"Videos\",\"idqSYA\":\"Design sales and marketing collaterals\",\"kFdLGQ\":\"Magnificent palace complex In the foreground, an ancient scroll with a dragon pattern unfurls. In the background, a red sky and auspicious clouds appear. Several golden birds soar in the sky, and red ribbons flutter.\",\"iLIErw\":\"Urdu\",\"8Yl2gw\":\"Page limit reached: document would exceed the maximum of {0} pages.\",\"rQbg5Q\":\"Not supported\",\"NHesfg\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any similar results. Try searching something related.\",\"6RTgEQ\":\"Publish as Brand Template. Turn this design into a reusable template for brand consistency.\",\"XzGvQg\":\"Arabic\",\"qAhpVA\":\"Yellow\",\"6kHbAA\":\"Creative miniature scene, huge persimmon Hanging from the branches. Children are climbing the trees with ladders to pick fruits, some putting them in baskets, others transporting them on carts. The background is an autumn orchard.\",\"TyV9HQ\":\"Attached videos must be {0} minutes or less in length.\",\"82SpGg\":\"Fashion\",\"QH3gGg\":\"Create new folder inside {0}\",\"HUokkQ\":\"Search uploads\",\"qAt+Jw\":\"Ask your admin to add all your brand assets in one place, so you and everyone can create with consistency.\",\"QQlG0g\":\"<strong>Colour shuffling is more precise now.</strong> With colour themes, you can apply brand colours to backgrounds, text, and elements.\",\"nsnIEQ\":\"Add a subheading\",\"4tfZtg\":\"Shuffle style\",\"bBHGRg\":\"Hiking up Mt. Everest\",\"LRgfHw\":\"Drop to move your image into <span class=\\\"{1}\\\">{0}</span>\",\"clkUrw\":\"Open in Projects\",\"kJT+qQ\":\"Help me brainstorm theme ideas\",\"MqKTQA\":\"Untitled template\",\"JvuZZg\":\"Unable to update folder permissions\",\"vSfK+A\":\"Apply elements to all pages\",\"shO/ZA\":\"Suggest ways to adapt my idea for a different audience\",\"c4M2lA\":\"Create an image of a simple skincare bottle with soft botanical shadows in the background\",\"eYIw9Q\":\"Starred\",\"tJVxgw\":\"YouTube Thumbnail\",\"+ojjfQ\":\"Create a video of a softly lit claymation scene, a rounded blue cat and a yellow dog sculpted from soft modeling clay stand on a pastel beige stage. Their arms hang low, their expressive faces animated with subtle blinking and downcast eyes. The dog’s tail droops as the cat gently leans forward, both sharing a quiet, concerned moment. The animation has handcrafted textures, soft shadows, and warm lighting — evoking the emotional depth of children’s animation with a charmingly imperfect, stop-motion esthetic.\",\"nmRL+A\":\"Bar chart\",\"EAGQlA\":\"Character limit reached\",\"DYkWqg\":\"Shapes are ready\",\"dKX9bA\":\"Add guidance for sizing, consistency, line weight\",\"P1SNqg\":\"Styles, colours, formats, or transforms text.\",\"aAy+og\":\"The colour “{0}” is already in this colour palette. Please choose a different colour.\",\"yRf7Ow\":\"Add Brand Templates\",\"Qrkevg\":\"Delete folder\",\"iPI4GQ\":\"Generate captions\",\"GG+Ugw\":\"as a colour sketch\",\"DMTQhg\":\"Describe what your brand voice achieves and when to use it\",\"PBqFog\":\"Tell me what you’d like to design together...\",\"bgGnuw\":\"Prepare a tactical document for a marketing campaign\",\"LwJDlQ\":\"Shapes\",\"EhBH4w\":\"Search emoji\",\"QkIt5Q\":\"Create an interactive categorisation game where students drag and drop items into correct buckets. Start with an example science game sorting animals into “Mammals,” “Reptiles,” and “Amphibians” with immediate feedback and progress tracking.\\n\\nAs a follow up ask me about: specific items to categorise, category names/themes, difficulty level, visual theme preferences, feedback style for correct/incorrect answers\",\"T3m3aQ\":\"Create a video in the golden light of early morning, a duck drifts across a tranquil lake cloaked in mist. Soft rays of sunlight pierce through tree branches and reflect on the still