 it.\",\"cv3Tww\":\"Search your content\",\"51hO8Q\":\"Venn\",\"mP+1Sw\":\"Create a playful EOFY sales promo\",\"jtKTcw\":\"High-definition food photography style, a Big Mac burger. Pure white background.\",\"JNyD/Q\":\"Search {0}\",\"GNus9A\":\"a tweet\",\"lH7+yg\":\"Ultra isn’t available right now.\",\"TxnPWg\":\"壮丽河山策马奔腾\",\"ftr4Nw\":\"Link folder to logos\",\"JRx5OQ\":\"Gradient\",\"FXw32g\":\"Discover content from\",\"SNHWGg\":\"There was an error on our end, we couldn’t load your Brand Templates. Try refreshing.\",\"mLjypA\":\"Describe your brand’s unique personality and how you communicate with your audience. Your voice is an important way to attract people to your brand, create connections, and build trust with them. For example, “our voice is confident, casual, and friendly.”\",\"hWygnw\":\"Try an example\",\"HMXBow\":\"Recommended photos\",\"XFXK2w\":\"Apply to all pages\",\"JwCTcw\":\"Popular music\",\"iXhfIg\":\"Design an instagram post to advertise my garage sale this weekend\",\"rJtY6A\":\"Hospitality and Leisure\",\"t/JPhw\":\"<strong>{0}</strong> is shared with <strong>{1}</strong> and <strong>{2, plural, one {# folder} other {# folders}}</strong>. Changes will be published immediately to everyone.\",\"2prKqA\":\"Custom merchandise\",\"aQA5wg\":\"Add guidance for sizing, pairings, hierarchy\",\"iMrZsw\":\"a summary report\",\"S4gFug\":\"LinkedIn Profile Picture\",\"qjp4Gw\":\"参考图中的宠物形象，生成史诗感宫廷大片，宏伟巴洛克宫殿内景（高挑拱顶、金色雕花柱廊、长窗透光），中央对称构图；宠物坐在奢华金色雕花王座上（红色天鹅绒靠背与坐垫），戴华丽的宝石王冠，胸前佩戴华丽宝石珍珠项链，披红丝绒白毛边披风；宠物开心的表情，拟人姿态翘着二郎腿，（拟人坐姿，上半身微后靠，后腿像人一样坐在座椅上；一条后腿伸直向前，一条后腿抬起并横跨压在另一条后腿膝盖上形成清晰“二郎腿”交叉，交叉点在膝盖位置；伸直向前的后腿脚掌朝向镜头）前爪自然搭在扶手上，镜头低机位仰拍，广角24mm，夸张近大远小，一只爪子十分靠近镜头，前景脚掌肉垫清晰可见；红色地毯延伸至画面下方，周围散落璀璨奢华的权杖、项链、打开的宝箱等许多金银珠宝首饰，金红主色调，暖金顶光+侧窗自然光，强烈高光与阴影层次，超写实摄影质感，毛发细节清晰，电影级调色。\",\"OyA28A\":\"Decorate\",\"odiAdQ\":\"Design\",\"YJs7vQ\":\"Circle\",\"KGvMow\":\"Creative\",\"VIzihw\":\"I need help creating a distinctive, memorable logo that captures my business’s essence and resonates with its audience. I want you to act as my graphic designer specialising in brand logos. Before we start designing anything, please ask me 3 focused questions selected from this list, one at a time to understand: 1. Business name & industry 2. Mission or core promise 3. Symbols, products, or ideas to convey 4. Brand personality (adjectives, vibe) 5. Visual preferences (minimal vs. detailed, serif vs. sans-serif, loved/avoided colours, reference logos) You MUST start your first response with a brief, professional introduction then move directly to the first question. Don’t use casual language like “Alright” or “Let’s dive right in!” - keep it professional and focused. Ask the questions one at a time and provide contextual suggestions when helpful based on previous answers. Please ask no more than three questions and then you should recommend creating a logo using the information (e.g. “Should I create an X for you now?”). Start with the most important question first. Keep your tone warm and conversational - like a trusted creative partner who knows how to make logos that work crisply in colour and black-and-white, scale from favicon to billboard, and stay timeless rather than trendy. Make sure the design matches the brand tone and values we uncover. Only add explanations for questions if it’s not obvious why that information would be needed. Guidelines for logo outputs Versatile: works crisply in colour and in black-and-white. Scalable: legible from favicon to billboard. Balanced: clean shapes, considered spacing. Timeless: simple over trendy; avoid fleeting fads. Brand-aligned: visuals match the tone and values you uncovered.RetryClaude can make mistakes. Please double-check responses.\",\"zVBC7A\":\"Dispersing gradient style\",\"SVJBEw\":\"Technology style\",\"mscrjg\":\"Choose the exact shades or use ready-made palettes to stay consistent and save time.\",\"zXnKTw\":\"Students will synthesize information from multiple generated news sources on a significant current event using the 5 Ws framework (Who, What, When, Where, Why). This activity should help students summarize, and distinguish between facts and opinions while developing critical reading skills.\",\"hk2NBQ\":\"Backgrounds can’t be used because Brand Controls are turned on for this folder\",\"vl2Wdg\":\"Add a title\",\"gHMNeQ\":\"Drop in clouds and simple sky shapes for a light, airy feel\",\"ZIE4zA\":\"Add a shape\",\"5PR6nw\":\"Add scrollable design\",\"kfyfhQ\":\"Frequently asked questions\",\"MZWFig\":\"Ask the creator to add all your brand assets in one place, so you and everyone can create with consistency.\",\"07WpEQ\":\"Generate ads\",\"txYRVA\":\"Celebrate an achievement or milestone\",\"gOitAg\":\"Search colour palettes\",\"1u3HbA\":\"Expand guidelines\",\"/PAXQQ\":\"in a 1:1 aspect ratio\",\"G4LALQ\":\"Create an image of a city skyline at dusk\",\"XtISPQ\":\"Good vibes only.\",\"bwZdqA\":\"Hand drawn illustration\",\"qZQC5A\":\"Create {1} featuring {0}\",\"83jLQQ\":\"Gallery\",\"BJZkVg\":\"Add to asset category\",\"+ue+Og\":\"Add a brand voice\",\"6qr2SA\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any {0, select, photos {photos} graphics {graphics} videos {videos} audio {audio} other {results}}{2, select, NO_CREATOR_NAME {} other { by {2}}} for “{1}”.\",\"k2qmJg\":\"Edit with Canva AI\",\"X2zEIg\":\"Create a video of a minimalist shot of a coupe glass filled with amber liquid, garnished with a coiled orange peel. The drink sits on a golden satin surface, with late-afternoon light casting rich highlights and soft shadows across the scene.\",\"rl6PEA\":\"Colours can’t be shuffled in a sheet\",\"U63igQ\":\"Bright red\",\"2SeT/w\":\"Search {0} templates\",\"bVM2tQ\":\"A steaming mug of coffee with heart latte art in a coffee shop\",\"nZVtww\":\"Styles\",\"2VpDSA\":\"Styles\",\"Qn66XA\":\"Cobalt blue\",\"WtY8RQ\":\"Recent\",\"Eoi2Cw\":\"I dislike this app\",\"VUCWHQ\":\"Black and white\",\"xUXK6A\":\"What would you like to write?\",\"DBROvg\":\"Add Brand Templates to this Brand Kit\",\"SQC