",\"nXFyFg\":\"This page type does not support captions\",\"2IT1dg\":\"Select videos with speech\",\"0kuIaw\":\"Fast\",\"WLNsSA\":\"Apply this set\",\"IxF/qg\":\"Create an image for me, elegant bamboo leaf silhouette logo, small teapot placed in the centre, symmetrical layout on the central axis, the colour is elegant dark green. The overall design style is simple and elegant, with oriental esthetics\",\"NmwAvQ\":\"I like this app\",\"m5sxiw\":\"Add colours\",\"+K1srg\":\"Styles can’t be used in Whiteboards\",\"mpS3Kg\":\"Minimalist Flat Style Girl Illustration\",\"4YfzNA\":\"in a text only style\",\"PPWvTg\":\"Balanced\",\"TMn6IQ\":\"Email\",\"fpBtAw\":\"Put some swirling galaxies and cosmic shapes throughout\",\"R/653Q\":\"To start adding elements to your design, start with a template or generate a design.\",\"VwyvXg\":\"Add this table to the canvas\",\"oCkOHg\":\"Create an interactive vocabulary matching game where students connect terms with definitions. Start with an example math vocabulary set featuring 6 geometry terms with colourful design, hint system, and celebratory animations for correct matches.\\n\\nAs a follow up ask me about: subject area, specific terms and definitions to include, difficulty level, visual theme preferences, hint/feedback style\",\"giIv0A\":\"Sorry, we can’t load images right now. Please reload the page, or use search.\",\"v6mXuw\":\"Delete\",\"ZC1MXw\":\"Cancel\",\"5TI84g\":\"Students will compare and contrast monarchy and democracy government systems, examining their structures, decision-making processes, and citizen roles. This activity should help students understand the advantages and disadvantages of different forms of government and their impact on citizens’ daily lives.\",\"DZBHFw\":\"See controls\",\"KhpzKQ\":\"Ask a teacher to set up\",\"rka5HQ\":\"This Brand Kit has an unsaved brand voice\",\"clTBAQ\":\"Discard\",\"QKQPPg\":\"Lines\",\"SM1Wtw\":\"Generate a hand-drawn illustration style learning check-in on Xiaohongshu\",\"fpWSDg\":\"Something went wrong. Please try again.\",\"SSb5mg\":\"Social media\",\"JsVejQ\":\"Format Flip: Turning Historical Events into Modern Media\",\"44yKvg\":\"Transfers assets to and from cloud storage, DAMs, or digital channels.\",\"u4zY9g\":\"Signature\",\"oJD2dw\":\"6-pointed star\",\"wl7Hfg\":\"Upgrade to access folders\",\"3moXcA\":\"Suggest ways to connect with my audience\",\"bItqMw\":\"Donut chart\",\"8fQJKg\":\"Apply Beautify result {0} of {1}\",\"WyYjWA\":\"Create a video of a stylish elderly man in a retro tee, wide-leg trousers, and mustard sneakers grooves to music in a cozy 1970s living room. He wears large headphones and dances freely in front of a wood-paneled wall, surrounded by framed art and warm tones.\",\"xqXR0g\":\"Slovak\",\"MgTXXQ\":\"Replace across designs\",\"x34XrQ\":\"A sorting activity for my class\",\"IPBHtw\":\"an outline\",\"LA3Kdg\":\"Create a video of a highly stylised 2D illustration of a black cat with off-white face and paws, caught mid-stride with elongated limbs and a sharp, sideways glare. The background is a vivid cobalt blue with no texture, emphasising the graphic silhouette. The artwork embraces flat colour fields, strong contour shapes, and visual humor. The scene is designed to feel like a frame from a cut-paper animation or a modern screen-printed poster — minimalist, offbeat, and confidently abstract.\",\"gR2aoQ\":\"Create forms or elements used in forms.\",\"C5CdBg\":\"Record a talking head\",\"hafjbw\":\"Create an image for me, “Double Eleven promotion, 50% off on all items” 3D platinum gradient font, subtitle “Hot sale limited time sale”, the text edge has a red-orange gradient highlight effect, e-commerce promotion font, white background\",\"6eK1QA\":\"Create a social media post featuring {0}\",\"9iKHPw\":\"feelings and experience\",\"927MoA\":\"Vector\",\"/8r6RQ\":\"Government affairs style\",\"0+bxqw\":\"<b>Deleting this category is permanent and cannot be undone.</b><br/> The assets and guidelines will no longer be available. Any linked content inside may still be accessed elsewhere.\",\"7QNV5w\":\"Create a video of a charming 3D character rendered entirely in felt, featuring plush, woolen textures and soft stitched details. The character has a rounded clay-red hairstyle, forest green felt glasses, and wears a mustard yellow jacket over a cream shirt. In a locked-off medium shot against a bright lavender background, the character reaches into their jacket pocket, pulls out a small felt phone, and taps on the screen with veracious focus. After a brief pause, their expression shifts - they smile brightly, slip the phone back into their pocket, and look up with a gleeful, satisfied expression. Lighting is soft and evenly diffused, highlighting the handcrafted seams, fabric softness, and stop-motion-inspired realism.\",\"WADKBg\":\"Audience\",\"eCIskQ\":\"Generates video or animated elements, or edits them using AI.\",\"H6/FcA\":\"Drop in ribbons and bursts for a celebratory feel\",\"5pX97g\":\"See all\",\"T3XLJA\":\"Show more\",\"vNmDmQ\":\"Generating AI voice\",\"nt/5Sw\":\"Promote a new business launch\",\"y2YCDQ\":\"Add Google Maps to your designs\",\"7kInDQ\":\"Audio\",\"bsiqIg\":\"Inside a mid-century modern apartment\",\"WpP9IA\":\"Add a quote\",\"O85ChA\":\"file conversion\",\"mgCLFA\":\"{0} (default)\",\"unHB7g\":\"Elegant Bamboo Leaf Silhouette Teapot Logo\",\"MrtHuA\":\"We were unable to add your file, as you’ve reached the maximum limit of {0} files for this brand ingredient\",\"kIz9iA\":\"Edit colors\",\"Ob8QTQ\":\"{0}/{1}\",\"ueH8+Q\":\"Retail\",\"l/b6tQ\":\"Elements are ready\",\"zchD7g\":\"Remove from folder\",\"oTLOog\":\"Shuffle\",\"/TMYXQ\":\"Add as new {0, plural, one {page} other {pages}}\",\"MiuOmQ\":\"Infographic\",\"fhD5lQ\":\"This app is in beta and may not work as expected.\",\"A41sTA\":\"Create a claymation sequence for a children’s short\",\"P7xpyQ\":\"Javanese\",\"Ek8xbg\":\"Open the Apps Marketplace and search for {0}.\",\"y0Co6A\":\"See all Tables\",\"nJ/rWw\":\"Magic Media\",\"qieicg\":\"Font combinations\",\"O39G2Q\":\"Components\",\"tpiwJw\":\"If you continue you will lose the changes you’ve made to your Brand Kit, how would you like to proceed?\",\"NnySAA\":\"30-pointed star\",\"ZC1s2A\":\"Lingala\",\"Nwle8Q\":\"“AI” Futuristic Tech Style Title\",\"Iakxug\":\"Reload\",\"bWYyIw\":\"Apply style to all pages\",\"xE4Gng\":\"Pentagon\",\"surO1w\":\"Hexagon\",\"+F+xJA\":\"Create a video of a static pop-art inspired composition featuring a close-up of a woman’s hand with glossy bubblegum purple nails, gently pinching a silver string suspending a shimmering disco ball. The disco ball’s mirrored surface scatters sharp highlights, including a radiant sparkle starburst. The background is a smooth, solid mint green, creating a clean high-contrast palette that channels retro poster design. Lighting is even and saturated, evoking the visual language of editorial cutouts or 1970s vinyl covers — crisp, iconic, and graphic.\",\"PKqHxA\":\"Find out what Canva for Slack can do for collaboration\",\"FdMEKA\":\"Good Result\",\"CYGC2w\":\"heatmap\",\"9GWcXg\":\"Applies a visual overlay, such as a filter, to the entire image.\",\"Ne9+Og\":\"This folder is full of potential. Photos and Elements you like will appear here.\",\"0igZvQ\":\"Add fonts to express your brand\",\"7dKf1Q\":\"I need help creating engaging, visually striking social media content that promotes my product on the right channels and gets people to take action. I want you to act as my social media marketing strategist. Before we start designing anything, please ask me 3 focused questions selected from this list, one at a time to understand: 1. Product features & key benefits 2. Price point or offer details 3. Priority platform(s) (Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, etc.) 4. Campaign goal & core message 5. Target audience (demographics & mindset) 6. Brand look & feel (tone, palette, references) You MUST start your first response with a brief, professional introduction then move directly to the first question. Don’t use casual language like “Alright” or “Let’s dive right in!” - keep it professional and focused. Ask the questions one at a time and provide contextual suggestions when helpful based on previous answers. Please ask no more than three questions and then you should recommend creating social media content using the information (e.g. “Should I create an X for you now?”). Start with the most important question first. Keep your tone warm and conversational - like a trusted creative partner who knows how to hook attention fast, follow platform best practices, spotlight product benefits clearly, and include strong calls-to-action. Make sure everything stays consistent with my brand. Only add explanations for questions if it’s not obvious why that information would be needed. Guidelines for content outputs Hook fast: grab attention in the first 1-2 seconds or first scroll-stop. Platform fit: follow channel best practices (short copy for Instagram, vertical video for TikTok, etc.). Benefit spotlight: surface the product win clearly and quickly. Clear CTA: tell viewers exactly what to do next. Brand consistency: stick to approved colours, fonts, and voice across assets.\",\"SCH0dw\":\"Armenian\",\"cDU7og\":\"Showing all marketplace videos\",\"LSX9+Q\":\"Videos\",\"urOqjw\":\"Ask your admin to define the default look of your charts, so your data always looks on brand.\",\"eL/cYA\":\"A Xiaohongshu note sharing the morning C and evening A skincare routine\",\"bGGWYg\":\"Promote my new bakery opening\",\"ckE5pw\":\"in an hand drawn illustration style\",\"7WBAog\":\"Email\",\"Prt1sQ\":\"Start with data\",\"ZGQVuA\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any text for “{0}”. Try searching something related.\",\"nKDWwA\":\"Modular\",\"gzmoJg\":\"Basque\",\"tQjI5w\":\"a project proposal\",\"zIXNlQ\":\"Sorry we couldn’t find any {0, select, graphics {graphics} emoji {emoji} logos {logos} other {results}} for “{1}”. Try searching something related.\",\"AcBc5w\":\"A4\",\"K68vOw\":\"Next\",\"BAkJxw\":\"More like this\",\"wP0yBA\":\"Draw\",\"U6k7MA\":\"Your change wasn’t saved because the Brand Kit was outdated, but it’s refreshed now. Try again.\",\"84ZfWA\":\"<strong>{0}</strong> is shared with <strong>{1}</strong>. Changes will be published immediately to everyone.\",\"xkZ8gw\":\"All videos\",\"CkMTSg\":\"Monoline\",\"f7wEKg\":\"Request access\",\"NxWsuQ\":\"Make your brand stand out with colours\",\"DzTKtg\":\"Colours\",\"mrXF5A\":\"Timeline\",\"v0HdHA\":\"Apply text style to all pages\",\"lQbQ1g\":\"Right now, only people with existing access to the folder <b>{0}</b> can <b>view</b> it. Share to let everyone with Brand Kit access also use this folder to stay on brand.\",\"YP9vXA\":\"Delete\",\"rFoW5g\":\"a Facebook cover photo\",\"OVj1tA\":\"How do I start using {0} in Canva?\",\"YU3+6w\":\"Workplace education & training\",\"qTgnOw\":\"E.g. make it look more modern, clean layout, brighter colours\",\"gaYg+g\":\"Apply style to all pages\",\"1EiqcQ\":\"Horizontal\",\"Kc4umg\":\"Media & news\",\"ibcJbQ\":\"Light blue\",\"7fDZlQ\":\"保持上图动物形象不变，生成一个鱼眼镜头视角的画面，戴鎏金帝王冠（红宝石、流苏），穿红底金纹财神华服（瑞兽、祥云），双爪抱金色钱袋，大眼睛微笑，站在走廊里；鱼眼超广角视角，轻微畸变，暗角效果，正中对称构图，主体居中，室内暖色氛围，主体背后是一面墙（米色/浅棕墙面），顶部有暖黄色灯光光斑与柔和虚化；地面为浅色瓷砖，远处暖黄色顶灯/壁灯形成柔和光斑与虚化。\",\"Q+mm5Q\":\"Continue\",\"udSNNg\":\"Page could not be added. Maximum of {0} pages.\",\"VUE4Kw\":\"Free\",\"Vu2cMg\":\"Create an audio clip featuring {0}\",\"byDvuA\":\"Magic Video\",\"7Q3lLQ\":\"Design an invite for a 90s-themed birthday party\",\"vC4k4g\":\"A QR code on top of an image of a house with a black and white background\",\"rpIdWg\":\"Describe your usage guidelines and principles\",\"zOgP6A\":\"You’re not able to delete this component. Reach out to your Brand Designer or team admin for help.\",\"9IZzNw\":\"Interactivity\",\"Bs1uTg\":\"All your brand’s logos in one place\",\"zlQcyA\":\"参考图中的人物形象生成马头人身拟人形象，只参考图中人物发型、配饰、服装；在办公室工位上，对着电脑吃着炸鸡；创意噪点摄影，胶片质感，慢快门动态残影，整体晃朦，褪色，轻微过曝，画面严重模糊，充满杂色颗粒，主体仅显轮廓、细节模糊，低饱和度\",\"U1OaeQ\":\"Add folder to {0}\",\"D6AYEA\":\"Sound effect\",\"JHeD2Q\":\"Graphics\",\"qjP2ww\":\"Ask your admin to add your brand voice so you can generate engaging content with consistency.\",\"66c+cA\":\"Photos\",\"URR9/w\":\"Forms\",\"9Ke+TQ\":\"Photo and video editing\",\"Nlq5Bw\":\"跨不过山，跨得过年\",\"ykyeag\":\"Turn on free filter\",\"8RJ9wQ\":\"data explorer\",\"g1UwTA\":\"Sheet\",\"tCfroA\":\"Provides access to social media or internal communication tools.\",\"yuHSrw\":\"Create a logo for {0}\",\"R5ER5g\":\"See more like this\",\"HZTK3A\":\"Original audio\",\"2tnvXw\":\"in a cartoon style\",\"EP8v5g\":\"in a playful style\",\"euBgXg\":\"Hand-drawn Style Character Picnic Scene Illustration\",\"6wUaBQ\":\"Academy style\",\"Hi7mzA\":\"Discard\",\"CFMXTw\":\"Professional\",\"VSXLQg\":\"Done\",\"IdLobQ\":\"with audio\",\"vi0vGg\":\"Trending\",\"NAOuOA\":\"See all\",\"4F0e+g\":\"Designing a custom background just for you, based on content from your page.\",\"uAtTQQ\":\"Apply both sections\",\"e5UD1Q\":\"Data autofill is not available on mobile\",\"dLrNzw\":\"Enables designs to be printed on materials like clothing and stationery.\",\"GTl5lA\":\"Come back to {0} to access and add more logos to your Brand Kit\",\"c2fW/w\":\"in a collage style\",\"yyN/5Q\":\"Create a Xiaohongshu design featuring a realistic-style pet care guide\",\"wYts2w\":\"A set of thin line style function icons, the order of the icons is: Album, music, shopping cart, alarm clock, notepad, map, car, clock, subway . Neatly arranged, white background\",\"k6b/Bw\":\"Code\",\"y+XZFg\":\"Help me create a cohesive design\",\"+kDWGA\":\"Add design\",\"hcWy2A\":\"Add folder\",\"isK6tQ\":\"Technology\",\"AlLoYQ\":\"Vintage film\",\"kZg7oA\":\"保持上图人物五官不变，仰视镜头，特写镜头，人物正脸清晰，神情坚定从容，英雄气质，身骑骏马；发型干净清爽，衣服为华丽汉服，衣摆与披风在画面边缘迎风飞扬。暗红骏马，马头完整，肌肉线条紧绷，鬃毛飞扬，金色马鞍局部可见。背景虚化呈现壮丽中国大好河山轮廓：群山、云海、江河抽象化层叠，红金主色调。前景红色飘带与灯笼强虚化形成光斑。\",\"Zo0sVw\":\"Social media content\",\"zyHh4A\":\"Good quality. Uses less of your AI limits.\",\"Cf