sound or voice using AI.\",\"8AtWVQ\":\"bump chart\",\"AKJwWQ\":\"Medium shot\",\"FMh6gw\":\"Dynamic text\",\"X59F2w\":\"You need edit and share access to a folder to add it\",\"lMqaMw\":\"Error: result could not be displayed\",\"0bJPmw\":\"<strong>{0}</strong> is shared with <strong>{1, plural, one {# folder} other {# folders}}</strong>. All changes, including deleted assets, are permanent, and this Brand Kit will be instantly updated. Proceed?\",\"nhkwDw\":\"Select the part of the design you’d like to replace.\",\"FMDpgw\":\"Search elements{1, select, NO_CREATOR_NAME {} other { by {1}}}\",\"eGL8zw\":\"Category name\",\"XIkOoA\":\"Generate a PPT for graduation defense. My topic is the application of artificial intelligence in education. The content includes research background, methods, results and conclusions.\",\"RlPZfg\":\"Access request sent\",\"Qa/kbw\":\"Cancel\",\"Rax2FA\":\"Pinterest Pin\",\"nAQocQ\":\"A 3D game exploring space\",\"M3+ayw\":\"This technology is new and improving. <a href=\\\"{0}\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">See terms</a>\",\"RvDvVg\":\"Surreal / dreamlike\",\"e1FCDg\":\"Add this poll to the canvas\",\"3vXMtg\":\"Delete font permanently\",\"8s45AQ\":\"Draft a journal entry from my future self in 10 years\",\"rIkNRA\":\"Note Outline\",\"jVvPCw\":\"2. On the floating toolbar, select <strong>More (...)</strong>.\",\"VfvO+Q\":\"Delete\",\"v4/yVg\":\"Galician\",\"WKPKKA\":\"A maximum of {0} bullet points are allowed. Please remove the extra points.\",\"r/pvAw\":\"Sinhala\",\"R+iBjQ\":\"Folder\",\"NGfbLQ\":\"Reload app\",\"sg09zA\":\"Delete\",\"ZrSzYg\":\"Shapes\",\"Jgx9qQ\":\"Code is ready\",\"7XxcCQ\":\"Report\",\"qftCZA\":\"Category: {0}\",\"RC8tvg\":\"Scatter tiny dots and dashes to add some texture\",\"64eg6A\":\"Add common mistakes to avoid for graphics\",\"m3bqMA\":\"Over-the-shoulder shot\",\"rPWE6Q\":\"Section added successfully\",\"JywJfA\":\"This app requires an update and is currently unavailable.\",\"kPBUeg\":\"Create folder\",\"txZEfA\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any {0, select, photos {photos} graphics {graphics} videos {videos} audio {audio} other {results}} for “{1}”. Try searching something related.\",\"VeylYQ\":\"in a minimalist style\",\"XkpzMw\":\"Edit themes\",\"G4R3yg\":\"Turn this design into a reusable template for brand consistency.\",\"JPP57w\":\"Lyrics in this language may not sound right.\",\"l2SnzQ\":\"Try again\",\"NyPMSA\":\"Toggle app options menu\",\"Ttngnw\":\"in a geometric style\",\"70gTGA\":\"Bad Result\",\"8H7kag\":\"Logo\",\"5+jEqw\":\"Marketing\",\"D0Qpvw\":\"Please wait a few minutes and try again.\",\"wjvYuQ\":\"AI quality\",\"TYFXjg\":\"<b>We couldn’t load your previously created QR codes.</b> Refresh the page and try again.\",\"vuYe0Q\":\"Character picnic scene The overall lines are simple, the colours are mainly black and white, with bright yellow embellishments. Hand-drawn style illustrations.\",\"0b5sYA\":\"Create an image of inside a mid-century modern apartment\",\"OEAoZw\":\"Call-to-action\",\"OZgZbA\":\"French\",\"J70Jfg\":\"Summary Report\",\"1DPhoA\":\"Facebook Cover\",\"Gm4yCg\":\"Horizontal hexagon\",\"9nPTKg\":\"Inverted trapezoid\",\"1Df0Xg\":\"Apply text only\",\"HLWJrQ\":\"More data sources\",\"vv7fUg\":\"Hand-drawn\",\"C2yIOA\":\"Marketing\",\"eaJZYQ\":\"We couldn’t delete {0}. Please retry.\",\"dGJ4vQ\":\"LinkedIn Post\",\"w3DGkQ\":\"Show the font styles for {0}\",\"4PxZFw\":\"Hand-drawn Line Art Style God of Wealth Illustration\",\"eHaULw\":\"As a {0} subscriber, you get this premium video for free.\",\"/6r9lw\":\"Audio can only be captioned in video page types with timeline view turned on.\",\"Dy9wjw\":\"Create learning materials\",\"0E+FFw\":\"Try creating in bulk on a desktop.\",\"4TpBCw\":\"Team apps aren’t reviewed by Canva. Make sure you trust it before using.\",\"dN9bEQ\":\"Woodcut engraving style with simple, bold lines. The upper body of a horse, with its hooves crossed over its chest, tilting its head with an expression full of confusion. Traditional Chinese New Year picture style, flat and cute, with a whimsical feel.\",\"LcOaoA\":\"Just exploring\",\"JLpbRg\":\"An error occurred.\",\"7C+INQ\":\"Create your first component\",\"nAiesQ\":\"Beta apps\",\"kvnRyg\":\"Here I Come (Tang Dynasty Style)\",\"ocYzkA\":\"A professional real estate listing ad\",\"vVm6nw\":\"3D Render\",\"Ed9ymQ\":\"Speech\",\"KYDbbQ\":\"Type\",\"u46yhA\":\"Grids\",\"5giVPg\":\"Invitation (A6)\",\"/cTpMA\":\"Create an image of a dog wearing a party hat\",\"gcyTsQ\":\"in a Chinese style\",\"TQh1GA\":\"Section\",\"EX0rcA\":\"Diamond\",\"Fq7Vmw\":\"Watercolour\",\"Xxlt3w\":\"Illustration\",\"U8SnRw\":\"No audio\",\"+7FAOA\":\"Clear\",\"/u4IKg\":\"1:1\",\"TgHjLQ\":\"Bokeh\",\"dGfBwg\":\"Create b-roll for a sustainability film\",\"GgPIpg\":\"Fresh and Elegant Food Photography\",\"mQd4rA\":\"Help me create a business plan PPT\",\"cHlCFw\":\"Design a logo for my organic juice bar\",\"ANACyw\":\"Create a music track featuring {0}\",\"3FzzUw\":\"Business\",\"2dMxfA\":\"Collage\",\"taJNaQ\":\"Playful\",\"MMEz3w\":\"arrow chart\",\"HNOlGA\":\"a blog post\",\"5Iz0Bw\":\"Analysing your media...\",\"S/4IoA\":\"Notice Announcement\",\"yguiUQ\":\"QR codes\",\"gF6+bA\":\"Audio\",\"PCEsDw\":\"To enter timeline view, select the relevant video page and click on the pencil icon.\",\"zCLtdA\":\"in a technology style\",\"Wcy4OQ\":\"Beta\",\"p8dDvg\":\"Brand voice\",\"B5wTOQ\":\"Description\",\"PJPEsw\":\"Saved for Offline\",\"qxT2lQ\":\"3D Cartoon Style Girl Giving Speech\",\"To2WbA\":\"Moody\",\"N2mt7Q\":\"Arrow block concave\",\"F9Y47Q\":\"Related searches\",\"+77qEQ\":\"<a data-anchor-id=\\\"upload\\\" href=\\\"#\\\">Upload media</a> to generate a video design\",\"4KRh8Q\":\"Cancel\",\"IW3GHQ\":\"Manage category\",\"2L/oZQ\":\"Upload\",\"+80c9w\":\"Delete\",\"DhO37w\":\"Free\",\"X7rjvw\":\"Your logos appear here\",\"ozHogw\":\"Labs\",\"T1QATA\":\"Request access\",\"FlpXNg\":\"This Brand Kit\",\"VspX5Q\":\"Create a video of a playful stack of rounded geometric shapes, each with a unique texture: smooth white marshmallow, glossy orange plastic, velvety red, bubbling violet gel, neon green sponge, and synthetic grass. Water droplets cling to some surfaces, adding tactile realism — clean, surreal, and colourful.\",\"9fATtQ\":\"No Brand Templates in this folder\",\"F5IexQ\":\"Data visualisation\",\"uOL2oQ\":\"Generate in this brand voice\",\"EA6NrQ\":\"Provides a library of royalty-free or custom sound effects, or generates them using AI.\",\"c0Qwlg\":\"Ray Traced\",\"Y8TTVg\":\"Create a video where a wide cinematic aerial shot glides over a pristine glacial lake wrapped in ethereal mist. Golden-hour sunlight streaks across the water’s glassy surface, painting it in soft amber and pink hues. Snow-dusted peaks encircle the lake, their reflections shimmering faintly in the fog. The camera slowly descends toward the lake’s edge, revealing a line of pine trees cloaked in silence. Audio: the faint call of distant birds and the whisper of wind rustling the treetops.\",\"lccCHw\":\"Detailed\",\"5yFiCg\":\"Keep\",\"Ntahpw\":\"It’s quiet now, but not for long...\",\"VMmYAA\":\"Add guidance for tone, vocabulary, key messages\",\"JmUmVA\":\"Provides a library of royalty-free images or generates them using AI.\",\"ISbKAA\":\"Apply to all pages\",\"PxgStQ\":\"A marketing ROI graph showing an upward trend with orange background\",\"lQoc5A\":\"Ask the creator to add brand assets so you and everyone can create with consistency.\",\"+CTQZg\":\"CMYK input\",\"Tm6W5g\":\"Delete\",\"MJGN1g\":\"Koalas sleep up to 22 hours a day? Talk about living the dream!\",\"RtlglA\":\"A 3D chibi plush-style gold ingot (yuanbao), rounded and adorable. A symmetrical ingot shape with a high raised center and naturally downward-curving sides. One consistent plush texture throughout. Predominantly yellow. Background: a soft gradient from warm red to creamy off-white. The atmosphere is cozy, festive, cute, and auspicious. Centered composition with generous negative space around the edges. No text.\",\"9EO7Yw\":\"Banners\",\"Si4+9A\":\"This developer has declared that they will comply with all applicable laws and regulations.\",\"iFoHEA\":\"This element cannot be added to your design. Please check that it still exists in {0}.\",\"EjcK/Q\":\"Get help from a brand designer to set up your Brand Templates.\",\"PwSnuQ\":\"Include the brand story, values, and standards on how to use each asset so your brand shines.\",\"QVkjLg\":\"Compose a poem about the sounds of a city at dawn\",\"z0wMBg\":\"Podcast Cover\",\"s0Q9pQ\":\"Add common mistakes to avoid for icons\",\"tkpJfQ\":\"You’ve used up your {0, number} characters for today. Come back tomorrow for more.\",\"PnUVfg\":\"with a close-up shot framing\",\"PvcUNA\":\"What is {0} in Canva?\",\"E2u2nQ\":\"参考图中的宠物形象，棚拍萌宠写真，竖版近景半身特写，微俯拍，宠物居中看向镜头，可爱开心的表情；宠物戴着红黄毛线钩织的可爱财神帽，脖子上戴着黄色格纹三角口水巾（多个番茄元素的小印花平铺）；画面两侧各有一只人手把两颗成熟大红番茄轻轻贴在宠物脸颊两边；背景为纯红色无纹理影棚背景，构图极简对称；均匀打光，低阴影、肤毛层次丰富，色彩高饱和但不过曝，商业广告级清晰度，真实摄影质感，高清细节，浅景深，主体全清晰。\",\"QZ4gow\":\"Educational\",\"WCKv/A\":\"Please select a font before saving\",\"NeE7Jw\":\"Smart Design\",\"juxEpQ\":\"AI images\",\"n4Ne7g\":\"YouTube Thumbnail\",\"NbKq/g\":\"Generate a realistic street exploration and travel life record on Xiaohongshu\",\"ATbBJA\":\"View\",\"E9T5CA\":\"Brand Kit\",\"4xRgMg\":\"Frames\",\"OprZqg\":\"Search shortcuts menu\",\"fZptog\":\"Magic recommendations\",\"+dmoaw\":\"Add your brand fonts\",\"5rMoSQ\":\"Sorry, there were no results for “{0}”\",\"gq0m9w\":\"Select a font size\",\"MZQTQA\":\"Guidelines options\",\"+hfc1Q\":\"Square\",\"5GyKuQ\":\"No brand logos set up yet\",\"PD8r8g\":\"Chinese (Mandarin, Taiwan)\",\"zzK3QQ\":\"Add this sheet to the canvas\",\"SZTxbg\":\"App promo graphics\",\"K1n8Qw\":\"An outline for a review of a podcast series\",\"/JmOvA\":\"Lime\",\"8leKmQ\":\"Apply text style to all pages\",\"2Y6E7g\":\"Select {1} {0, select, graphic {graphic} shape {shape} frame {frame} photo {photo} element {element} other {media}}\",\"p8r7aQ\":\"sunburst\",\"P/lT9A\":\"Search font sets\",\"m5a1hw\":\"Tweet\",\"C9DfFg\":\"Maintain brand consistency by setting up ready-to-use templates.\",\"njkJ/w\":\"Graphics\",\"4PrxCw\":\"Create an image of a delicious, healthy pasta dinner\",\"KZnNoQ\":\"Summary\",\"vZlw9g\":\"Design\",\"d89U1g\":\"You can upload multiple .PNGs, .JPGs, .SVGs, .WEBPs, .AVIFs and .HEIC/HEIFs.\",\"WCZAmQ\":\"Try autofilling data for other design categories, such as presentations\",\"R0+/Kg\":\"Styles\",\"N7uy8g\":\"Don’t\",\"oQcNaw\":\"Portuguese\",\"v6aTTg\":\"Captions aren’t available for this type of design.\",\"UgwgeQ\":\"Report this result\",\"IvlKQQ\":\"Pashto\",\"mc8DTg\":\"an attractive header\",\"OgrTBA\":\"Browse categories\",\"COuT6g\":\"See all\",\"2vDKEA\":\"Subheadings\",\"7+xagw\":\"Minimalist Art Style Skincare Product Photography\",\"KKVOvA\":\"Stars\",\"GRo+Qg\":\"A voiceover script for a Douyin video titled “Challenge to Eat in Shanghai for a Day with 100 Yuan”\",\"VaTLPg\":\"<strong>{0}</strong> is shared with <strong>your organisation</strong> and <strong>{1, plural, one {# folder} other {# folders}}</strong>. Changes will be published immediately to everyone.\",\"kTzpFQ\":\"Add your brand fonts\",\"J/ihzw\":\"You do not have view access\",\"ntth2Q\":\"Nepali\",\"SQ579w\":\"Students will evaluate the transition to renewable energy sources, forming evidence-based opinions on clean power implementation and policy. This activity should develop students’ ability to analyze complex environmental and economic issues while supporting their positions with scientific evidence.\",\"vN0a2Q\":\"4:3\",\"nOHxWA\":\"Create an abstract background for a modern arts festival\",\"HrvPCw\":\"17-pointed star\",\"xb2ZjQ\":\"Help me create a university graduation defense PPT\",\"tEAYSw\":\"Edit palettes\",\"LQWBLg\":\"Edit footage like a pro with motion effects, subtitles, and quality enhancing tools.\",\"2flIiA\":\"Edit guidelines\",\"JjrO4w\":\"Turkmen\",\"fTBymA\":\"Import data\",\"6XdsSg\":\"Sketch\",\"59CIrw\":\"Tables\",\"RNmAjg\":\"Highest quality, great for images and video.\",\"OhJgKA\":\"“Life is Long, There Are Answers” Literary Handwriting Font\",\"0NG5Bg\":\"Arrow left\",\"AoxZ9g\":\"Text effects\",\"/qTAVQ\":\"Hebrew\",\"IhPRgA\":\"Create an intro clip for a calming, meditation app\",\"Sb70XQ\":\"Album Cover\",\"khSMZQ\":\"<strong>These results have been restricted by your administrator.</strong><br/>Contact them to learn more, or try searching for something else.\",\"/8bINQ\":\"A humorous and sincere student union election PPT outline\",\"17hobQ\":\"See what you can do with AI\",\"0gK5EQ\":\"Create a Xiaohongshu design featuring hand-drawn illustrations about workplace anxiety among office workers\",\"8/xJKg\":\"Occitan\",\"xdD6Lg\":\"Good storytellers paint pictures with words; great ones bring them to life.\",\"e89RrA\":\"Draft a Canva doc about {0}\",\"MvilDw\":\"Regenerate voiceover\",\"45frIQ\":\"You can add up to <strong>{0, plural, =0 {items} one {{0} item} other {{0} items}}.</strong>\",\"AO/PZg\":\"Magic Background\",\"yaTfgA\":\"Create a video of a cheerful composition spelling out “EOFY Sale” in plump, hand-modeled letters crafted from smooth matte plasticine in soft pink. Each letter is slightly irregular, giving the impression of being gently shaped by hand. The words are embedded in a grid of vibrant clay flowers, stars, and blobby shapes in canary yellow, sky blue, tangerine, and apple green — all rendered with velvety, non-reflective finishes. The entire layout is playful and uplifting, like a physical sculpture made for a storefront window or kid’s magazine spread. Lighting is soft and even, enhancing the material’s subtle seams and finger-molded impressions.\",\"l9jSKA\":\"参考图中的形象生成动物写真，穿着红底金纹财神帽和同色系红金刺绣财神服；优雅端坐敞口复古皮箱里，一手托鎏金元宝、一手握烫金红包，笑脸；红金背景，皮箱周围堆烫金红礼盒，散落春联、福字、中国结；传统招财意象，画面璀璨年味浓，高清写实风格\",\"j8lCzA\":\"Add a sticky note\",\"wYMlNg\":\"Add asset category\",\"LqqSUQ\":\"Plush Gold Ingot Bag\",\"SMB+gQ\":\"Traditional Chinese ink painting of a steed. The horse is depicted using varying densities of ink tones, reflecting Xu Beihong’s “xieyi” (freehand) brushwork style. Xuan paper texture with natural ink wash and halo effects.\",\"K+ClJQ\":\"Drop in cute animals and characters for a fun, playful look\",\"1lzb7g\":\"content scheduling\",\"Bh6MDg\":\"interactive design\",\"JicNaw\":\"Describe what your icons represent and when to use them\",\"fs1dFg\":\"Styles can’t be used in Sheets\",\"7H1GTA\":\"AI quality ({0})\",\"xRJbnw\":\"<b>We couldn’t load all of your previously created QR codes.</b> Refresh the page and try again.\",\"OtoP2g\":\"Logos\",\"r/V0Xg\":\"Logos will appear here once they are set up by an admin\",\"AzYIow\":\"Describe what your fonts express and when to use them\",\"o2PCew\":\"Create a design featuring {0}\",\"JDhOzw\":\"Design an invitation to invite friends to my cozy and welcoming housewarming, featuring autumnal colours and a picture of a house\",\"HIIBWA\":\"Chinese city landmark illustration, showcasing natural and cultural landscapes. Hand-drawn gradient style, Chinese trend.\",\"P+zlUg\":\"Thesis Outline\",\"q36TZg\":\"Creates dynamic content that responds to input.\",\"mUQTeQ\":\"Create an SVG-based digital celebration card with modern animations. Start with an example birthday card for “Emma” featuring confetti animations, a soft blue-to-pink gradient background, and interactive elements that trigger when clicked.\\n\\nAs a follow up ask me about: recipient name and celebration type, preferred colour palette (2-3 colours), message to display, animation style preferences\",\"b7KE1Q\":\"Icons for Gmail, Google Drive, Calendar and other Google Workspace apps with a blue “Install” button\",\"CsbGZw\":\"Agenda\",\"OllBDQ\":\"Apps you use will appear here for easy access.\",\"RFFX6A\":\"Generate AI voice\",\"tfviwQ\":\"Try “Blue” or “Pastel”\",\"ytHbGQ\":\"Yes, {0} is free to use with any Canva plan.\",\"eLrV2g\":\"Language\",\"QNQNNw\":\"Something went wrong. Please try again.\",\"A1VINA\":\"Charts\",\"SWvU5Q\":\"I need help creating a thoughtful, eye-catching design that celebrates a milestone and resonates with the intended audience. I want you to act as my graphic designer who specialises in celebrating special moments. Before we start designing anything, please ask me 3 focused questions selected from this list, one at a time to understand: 1. The milestone or achievement 2. The people involved and why it matters 3. The share format (Instagram post, printed card, poster, etc.) 4. The desired visual and emotional vibe (playful vs. formal, vibrant vs. muted, text-heavy vs. minimal) You MUST start your first response with a brief, professional introduction then move directly to the first question. Don’t use casual language like “Alright” or “Let’s dive right in!” - keep it professional and focused. Ask the questions one at a time and keep each question short and direct. Provide contextual suggestions when helpful based on previous answers. Please ask no more than three questions and then you should recommend creating a celebration design using the information (e.g. “Should I create an X for you now?”). Start with the most important question first. Keep your responses brief and focused - like a trusted creative partner who knows how to spotlight key messages with clarity and emotion, match the tone to the milestone, and create clean layouts optimised for sharing. Address me directly and end each reply with one clear next step. Only add explanations for questions if it’s not obvious why that information would be needed. Guidelines for celebration outputs Keep an impactful focus by spotlighting the key message with clarity and emotion. Ensure the tone matches the nature of the milestone. Add meaningful details such as names, dates, or numbers when they enhance the piece. Maintain a clean layout with plenty of breathing room and no clutter. Make the design share-ready and optimised for the chosen platform or medium.\",\"S7uScA\":\"Tell me what you’d like to design together...\",\"QSNvyw\":\"line chart race\",\"yCCf5Q\":\"Frames\",\"M6L36g\":\"Effects\",\"MFc1ag\":\"in a moody style\",\"zqSiTw\":\"You’ve reached your plan’s monthly AI usage limit.\",\"Jxi/KQ\":\"To apply individual brand colours, select an element and choose from the palette.\",\"p14vww\":\"Guidelines\",\"hLuHcA\":\"Manage Brand Kit\",\"Sl7p3w\":\"Apply colours together as a theme\",\"7JErew\":\"I need help creating a powerful, visually compelling design that raises awareness and drives engagement for a cause I care about. I want you to act as my communications designer who specialises in designing material that helps advocate for important causes. Before we start designing anything, please ask me 3 focused questions selected from this list, one at a time to understand: 1. What the issue or cause is 2. Why the cause matters 3. What action the audience should take 4. Which platforms will be used to share the piece 5. Who the audience is 6. Preferred tone and visual style (bold vs. gentle, text focus vs. imagery focus, colour choices, campaigns I admire) You MUST start your first response with a brief, professional introduction then move directly to the first question. Don’t use casual language like “Alright” or “Let’s dive right in!” - keep it professional and focused. Ask the questions one at a time and keep each question short and direct. Provide contextual suggestions when helpful based on previous answers. Please ask no more than three questions and then you should recommend creating advocacy content using the information (e.g. “Should I create an X for you now?”). Start with the most important question first. Keep your responses brief and focused - like a trusted creative partner who knows how to lead with emotionally resonant messages, make clear calls to action, balance facts with storytelling, and use accessible design that aligns with the cause’s ethics. Address me directly and end each reply with one clear next step. Only add explanations for questions if it’s not obvious why that information would be needed. Guidelines for design outputs Lead with an emotionally resonant message or visual. Make the call to action clear and actionable. Balance facts with storytelling to build urgency and empathy. Use accessible colours, fonts, and language for broad reach. Keep visuals aligned with the tone and ethics of the cause, avoiding exploitation or sensationalism.RetryClaude can make mistakes. Please double-check responses.\",\"GPZHWw\":\"Recently used\",\"KitgVg\":\"Write a blog post about caring for houseplants\",\"H3NGOQ\":\"Create an Image of snowboarding on a powder day\",\"zzsueQ\":\"in a cyberpunk style\",\"19WHfQ\":\"Create a video of a cluster of glossy lavender and coral balloons drifts slowly against a flat teal backdrop, all viewed through clear vertical ribbed glass. The glass surface bends and displaces the balloons’ forms — peaks, ripples, and soft shears stretch and compress their outlines as they shift behind the grooves.\",\"w4Bewg\":\"Drag and drop to upload files here. PNG, SVG and JPG are accepted formats\",\"swjx/g\":\"财神碰杯局\",\"b5HGvQ\":\"Add your brand colours\",\"Guvfhg\":\"Your QR codes\",\"wJFy7w\":\"rendered with ray tracing\",\"4SDG/Q\":\"Tamil\",\"kImUyQ\":\"Create an image of {0} {1} {2}\",\"wgA9Ag\":\"Failed to rename section\",\"3fiHVw\":\"Tatar\",\"qFoH8Q\":\"<strong>{0}</strong> is shared with the <strong>{1} team</strong> and <strong>{2, plural, one {# folder} other {# folders}}</strong>. All changes, including deleted assets, are permanent, and this Brand Kit will be instantly updated. Proceed?\",\"lfOWQw\":\"Transfers or analyses data from an off-platform database.\",\"Aii8jg\":\"Chinese\",\"Ye+2mA\":\"Documents\",\"JTKqvQ\":\"Create a logo for my business\",\"y+z94w\":\"Generated with AI. <a data-anchor-id=\\\"report-link\\\" href=\\\"{0}\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Let us know if this isn’t appropriate.</a>\",\"Chs0fQ\":\"Brand Assist\",\"0vDwMA\":\"Arrow block convex\",\"2/eOCg\":\"Yiddish\",\"PmkQJQ\":\"参考图中的人物形象生成马头人身拟人形象，只参考图中人物发型、配饰、服装；在白色背景的室内，手持白色 iPhone 14 Pro 手机对自拍，镜面反射出电梯金属质感的门壁，写实风格，光线均匀自然，画面清晰，主体突出，背景简洁干净。画面充满杂色颗粒，主体仅显轮廓、细节模糊，低饱和度\",\"3IrCnQ\":\"拜见大王\",\"qRIDew\":\"仅参考图中的宠物形象，宠物用爪子在手机自拍的一张随手拍照片，宠物开心的表情。萌宠超近景占画面大半部分，没有明确的主体和构图感，照片带有较强的动感模糊，手机前置广角。宠物戴着一个迷你的红色财神帽，佩戴红色粗圆框镜框，无镜片，脖子系红色围巾。宠物头部被广角透视夸张放大，背景在上海外滩前，夜雾/薄霾氛围，有许多人在主角背后行走虚化，人山人海，城市灯光散景光点，轻微手持抖动，轻胶片颗粒与噪点，轻微曝光过度，整体呈现一张刻意的平庸感。\",\"7FS2ZA\":\"村花姐妹过新年\",\"NREZdg\":\"Add to {0}\",\"ED00TQ\":\"You’ve applied a premium template\",\"fg6gtw\":\"Add brand guidelines to stay consistent\",\"IXdkjQ\":\"Turn any design into a template you can reuse anytime. Create once, stay on brand forever.\",\"HDNm8Q\":\"Design is ready\",\"O4ji0Q\":\"a Twitter post\",\"HncyHw\":\"To generate captions, make sure the media in your design has clear speech.\",\"EzezbQ\":\"Commercial & professional services\",\"KX8maA\":\"Rectangle\",\"IIHL4A\":\"Make sure you’ve tested how they look first.\",\"bcGJGA\":\"“You look interesting” The font design is lively and smart, with smooth and slightly curved lines, sans serif font, very modern, with green embellishment, white text on black background\",\"BY3YUg\":\"Create a Xiaohongshu design featuring a hand-drawn illustration style learning check-in\",\"DCeQVw\":\"Custom duration\",\"THUCfg\":\"Add new\",\"vFVlYQ\":\"Data Connectors\",\"Dn9Trw\":\"Colours\",\"pF0XZg\":\"Logos\",\"QZEq0Q\":\"Lucky bag (Fudai), mouth slightly open with a golden rope knot bow. New Chinese auspicious style with a 3D illustration texture. Rounded shape, translucent glowing texture, red and gold colour scheme. Smooth surface with soft highlights against a white background.\",\"V43vug\":\"You reached the limit of colour palettes for this Brand Kit.\",\"FIE5LQ\":\"A simple skincare bottle with soft botanical shadows in the background\",\"c2LyDA\":\"8-pointed star\",\"GvJnhQ\":\"Want audio?\",\"iuJq9Q\":\"