such as social posts and presentation\",\"K0uHew\":\"Sprinkle tiny hearts and stars for a sweet, cheerful look\",\"YUMSTQ\":\"Grain\",\"bcCKDA\":\"Caption\",\"2ucIkQ\":\"Students will investigate problems in current school cafeteria systems and develop comprehensive solutions for healthier, more efficient food service. This activity should integrate knowledge of nutrition, budgeting, and logistics while encouraging creative problem-solving skills.\",\"hQzffA\":\"Shanhaijing theme Chinese style painting style, horse , matte texture base, thick colour block brushstrokes, ancient style watercolour thick coating, rock colour craft.\",\"VJJlvw\":\"Request access to folders\",\"DrQT/w\":\"Audio ({0})\",\"mrXDAw\":\"A cat playing with a ball of yellow yarn\",\"BhxJFQ\":\"Apply bold brush strokes for an editorial look\",\"SVxujw\":\"Now, tell me a little more about your design...\",\"5cQROA\":\"A cover image for my travel vlog in Tokyo\",\"ERNrJg\":\"No chart styles added\",\"Y2hsHA\":\"Brand Template\",\"L69/Yw\":\"This folder is full of potential. Photos and Elements you like will appear here.\",\"KQyW7A\":\"a social post\",\"4u+qdA\":\"Learning and academic environments\",\"ZY72qg\":\"Learn how app <permissions-link>permissions</permissions-link> work in Canva.\",\"9cQCjw\":\"Phone Wallpaper\",\"nH+vfA\":\"Invite friends to my cozy housewarming\",\"urzTwQ\":\"Generate images for <strong>{0}</strong>\",\"8ztvyw\":\"Royal blue\",\"xmzGaw\":\"Custom\",\"/9lTBA\":\"Square\",\"Flx+pw\":\"Line chart\",\"oiDTZw\":\"See all\",\"gXic6Q\":\"Create a modern “build your own order” interactive menu without images. Start with an example for “Bella Cucina” featuring appetisers ($8-12), pastas ($14-18 with protein add-ons), and desserts ($6-9). Use clean typography and colour-coding instead of photos for a sophisticated look. Do not include “Place Order” or other non-functional buttons.\\n\\nAs a follow up ask me about: my restaurant name/concept, food categories and customisation optio