g a cinematic wide shot of a shadowed mountain range at dusk, silhouetted against a vivid red-orange sky streaked with fading light. Below, the ocean ripples with subtle motion, reflecting the fiery gradient above in molten crimson tones. A lone bird arcs gracefully across the sky near the upper right of frame, accentuating the vastness of the scene. The camera holds steady, capturing the stark contrast and moody stillness—evocative, intense, and minimal, with high-saturation lighting and a dramatic, almost apocalyptic tone.\",\"e+aUFA\":\"{0} has unsaved logos\",\"nVYe4Q\":\"Upgrade to get {0} of storage.\",\"RNBgvg\":\"Round speech bubble\",\"QAlhJQ\":\"This action is permanent and cannot be undone.\",\"2rMgBA\":\"a card\",\"9DLEKg\":\"Equilateral triangle\",\"Fbrovg\":\"See all Charts\",\"DK8ZEg\":\"Search Apps\",\"C4ABDg\":\"Dark Turquoise\",\"AFg7qQ\":\"{0, plural, one {# image} other {# images}} added to the Brand Kit\",\"2sPKlA\":\"Please save/discard your current changes\",\"VJR/Fg\":\"Search templates\",\"lc616w\":\"Cinematic Concept\",\"s51Y4w\":\"Completed\",\"UaBeVg\":\"Lady with Parasol Theme Oil Painting\",\"Kr20Ew\":\"timeline\",\"wRneVg\":\"Select media\",\"xPys3g\":\"Assets ({0})\",\"V4ftlw\":\"a strategic planning\",\"0SkUVw\":\"Mockups\",\"H5kV/g\":\"Shuffle style\",\"NHyJQg\":\"Spanish\",\"w/FEeQ\":\"Business Card (US)\",\"y/T4/A\":\"Build your brand identity, create campaign assets, and launch them to any channel.\",\"P2G1bA\":\"高级感骏马合照\",\"8/DMNA\":\"Text\",\"kcmV7g\":\"Add common mistakes to avoid\",\"+Q8erA\":\"Pro\",\"pgsRRA\":\"a thesis outline\",\"XSkKEg\":\"All Brand Templates\",\"rkud5Q\":\"an infographic\",\"rtgmTQ\":\"Add CMYK\",\"tygS4Q\":\"Try autofilling data on a desktop\",\"v/GXsA\":\"参考图中的宠物形象，宠物向镜头伸出一只爪子在手机自拍，随手拍照片，强烈的运动模糊，开心的表情看向镜头。宠物靠在夜晚江边栏杆边，远处城市灯光散景与水面反光；图片占比60%是宠物的头部特写，头戴可爱的红色贝雷帽，脖子围蓬松的红色针织围巾；爪子举着一根仙女棒烟花，靠近镜头爆闪，火花四溅形成强烈光斑与炫光，背景夜空中盛放大型烟花（长尾流星状火花、薄薄烟雾），烟花虚化散景；整体冷蓝夜景环境光+暖金火花强烈冷暖对比，浅景深，胶片质感、细颗粒、手持抖动，轻胶片颗粒与噪点，轻微曝光过度。\",\"3zXeOQ\