rom a starting point with brand assets and layouts ready, not from scratch.\",\"exz4Xg\":\"Bar chart\",\"a5yXdw\":\"Ask your admin to define your colour palettes to help you stay consistent and save time across designs.\",\"acGF/g\":\"No colours added\",\"UDcZRw\":\"a note outline\",\"rjLDVQ\":\"Create custom merchandise\",\"/tZKTg\":\"Come back to {0} to access and add more fonts to your Brand Kit\",\"Kr2Ydw\":\"Blog post\",\"eidDNA\":\"Graphics\",\"KcJWHQ\":\"Yes, {0} is free to use with paid Canva plans, as well as {1} and Nonprofit. Some apps require a Business plan or a separate subscription. Try {0} to check its requirements.\",\"puSVmA\":\"Map\",\"vtVhsA\":\"Hexagon\",\"w0YJxw\":\"Details\",\"2ra62Q\":\"Add best practices and preferred usage\",\"azRKfw\":\"Feelings and Experience\",\"TLzPzg\":\"Amharic\",\"ljgaDQ\":\"Delete Brand Kit\",\"RYxpYA\":\"text generation\",\"JvUl/g\":\"Business Card\",\"3UP/XA\":\"Finance & insurance\",\"MSCGJQ\":\"Catching Horse\",\"v7hkJA\":\"Zoom Virtual Background\",\"wNaqaQ\":\"This app isn’t available on mobile devices.\",\"pOV6og\":\"9:16\",\"tPrGPA\":\"Heading\",\"iuHYXA\":\"Earth Savers: Designing Solutions to Stop Erosion\",\"8Gah2g\":\"Show less\",\"ESTNGA\":\"{0, plural, one {# item} other {# items}}\",\"vPABKA\":\"3D models are ready\",\"NWgINw\":\"Write a review of a book series you recently discovered\",\"tfBMYQ\":\"参考图中人物形象复古新年写真，不要改变人物的五官，两人并肩站立，身体微微靠近，正对镜头微笑，整体姿态自然放松，人物身穿带有小碎花图案的红色系棉质上衣，服装风格偏传统朴素，具有年代感与生活气息。头巾自然包裹头部并垂于两侧，左侧人物佩戴红色头巾，发型为麻花辫，右侧人物佩戴绿色头巾，齐肩短发。左侧人物手拿巨大的“福”字门贴，右侧人物双手端着一个编织草篮，篮中放置柿子和橘子。背景为纯红色喜庆背景，带有细腻的金色粉尘/金粉颗粒效果，整体具有年画与宣传照质感。光线为柔和均匀的摄影棚打光，面部光线自然，肤质真实细腻，无过度磨皮。\",\"ZWPkPw\":\"3 - Good\",\"yRplkw\":\"Search Graphics Pro\",\"Da5Aog\":\"Full-body anthropomorphic brown horse figure with a festive smiling expression. Wearing traditional Chinese God of Wealth attire, ornate and exquisite, primarily in red and gold. Wearing an ancient Chinese God of Wealth official hat in a red and gold colour scheme. The horse’s right front hoof points towards the camera with exaggerated, dynamic action; the left front hoof holds a red vertical Spring Festival couplet scroll with gold text reading “指定发财” (Guaranteed Fortune). Overall theme: Spring Festival, New Year, and God of Wealth. Ultra-clear realistic style with photorealistic texture against a pure white background. Aspect ratio 3:4.\",\"TwxMNQ\":\"Add a little bit of body text\",\"n8HXgw\":\"An interactive historical timeline\",\"5ybcQA\":\"Green\",\"Y+rebA\":\"Triangle\",\"8vVC5A\":\"Decide for me\",\"pws+ig\":\"Set up your Brand\",\"0/7Tfw\":\"Asset category renamed\",\"FbjJtg\":\"Projects\",\"uNjU0g\":\"Audio and voiceover\",\"R5UUwg\":\"Ask your admin to add the right logos so everyone can use them with confidence.\",\"+1RfCA\":\"Upgrade to make videos using AI\",\"YmKtEg\":\"See more like this\",\"lOGZ3Q\":\"Videos with sound require <a data-anchor-id=\\\"try-ultra\\\" href=\\\"#\\\">Ultra quality</a>.\",\"vr2KHw\":\"Jungle green\",\"H5WH8w\":\"Delete the section, {0}?\",\"eBglFQ\":\"Ask the creator to add your brand voice so you can generate engaging content with consistency.\",\"ClIzxw\":\"Photos\",\"fjGcuQ\":\"Remove from {0}\",\"VvpevA\":\"Create an image of a cute work desk setup\",\"8lFeMw\":\"Audio\",\"aB1gXw\":\"Could not save changes to Brand Kit. Please try again.\",\"c8ESeA\":\"Please add more data and try again. No credits were used for this query.\",\"4+Wleg\":\"Add brand assets\",\"u6haRg\":\"No brand fonts set for this Brand Kit\",\"2bdGDA\":\"Which of these <span>work goals</span> can we help you reach?\",\"WV8iLA\":\"Apps and Integrations\",\"qjr7RA\":\"Frames\",\"VjhKGg\":\"Is {0} safe?\",\"uo1eBA\":\"Coral red\",\"47U++w\":\"Delete course\",\"FETFBg\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any music for “{0}”. Some tracks, including our popular music library, are not available for all plans or locations. Try searching something related or <a data-anchor-id=\\\"clear-filters\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\">clear filters</a>.\",\"XYSq9Q\":\"Students will practice close reading by examining an excerpt from Abraham Lincoln’s Gettysburg Address, first reading for general understanding, then re-reading to discover deeper meanings, literary devices, and historical context. The Gettysburg Address will be provided as the text for analysis. This activity should strengthen students’s ability to extract multiple layers of meaning from a single text and understand how word choice and structure contribute to a speech’s power and lasting impact.\",\"b982oA\":\"Graphics are ready\",\"Y8X7WQ\":\"Please wait a few minutes and try again.\",\"+8wRTA\":\"Instagram Story\",\"jGTTLQ\":\"Cut-out\",\"UNmVrg\":\"Animated\",\"zfehHw\":\"Tracks from the popular music library are only available to teams with 10 users or fewer.\",\"4ltq0w\":\"We were unable to add your file. Please try again.\",\"J3LhqA\":\"Marketing & advertising\",\"MOdGuQ\":\"Find all your components in one place\",\"ON5Mbg\":\"Don’t share\",\"Js5vyQ\":\"Showing elements that are free for you\",\"RnyGIQ\":\"Rename Brand Kit\",\"hrJQkg\":\"Icelandic\",\"kTdaNw\":\"with a custom duration\",\"CSdbnw\":\"A digital birthday card that explodes confetti\",\"cIAKgA\":\"3D\",\"4LHOmw\":\"Text styling\",\"Mbj4gw\":\"in {0, select, photos {Photos} graphics {Graphics} videos {Videos} audio {Audio} other {All}}\",\"HuIKXA\":\"Strategic Planning\",\"wwzBpg\":\"Create signatures\",\"WHzCNg\":\"Apply Magic Background result {0} of {1}\",\"4pBzXA\":\"Generate captions\",\"aLYjAQ\":\"with soft lighting\",\"A6QNjQ\":\"Gujarati\",\"BunKjw\":\"Remove from device\",\"romVzA\":\"No styles available\",\"WY3hlQ\":\"Failed to load styles\",\"xDNMag\":\"4 - Strong\",\"bnFfUQ\":\"白色骏马，构图为马的上半身，水彩混合，暖色轻松、色彩丰富，金粉点缀。神秘氛围+暖色奇景+明亮背景，中式群山环绕马身，金色流云穿梭。笔触灵动\",\"JsJtOw\":\"Grids\",\"uSi1qQ\":\"Select pages to add\",\"neWUNw\":\"Colours can’t be shuffled in an email\",\"KpP7Zg\":\"You are about to open <b class=\\\"{1}\\\">{0}</b> in a new tab.\",\"u+xgNA\":\"Empty folder image displayed when there are no installed apps\",\"F+IPBQ\":\"We found the following results for “{0}” in Elements:\",\"+oVOrA\":\"Styles\",\"REnnUg\":\"Scatter small floral accents to soften the page\",\"ljEAxQ\":\"Apple Horse\",\"OpV9AA\":\"Clear\",\"BKRqqQ\":\"Communicate on brand with chart styles\",\"Q5jyOg\":\"At least one media must be attached for video generation.\",\"UGL6FQ\":\"Cancel\",\"BkwLOQ\":\"保持上图宠物形象不变，可爱创意美食主题：俯拍视角，宠物身体完整地坐在一只白色陶瓷汤勺中，汤勺放置在浅色陶瓷碗里；碗中盛有浅色汤汁，汤内漂浮着多颗白色圆形汤圆；每一颗汤圆上都嵌入同一只宠物的真实头像贴图，宠物头像表情各不相同，但都是同一只宠物的形象；汤圆表面光滑细腻，带有少量金色桂花点缀，整体画面色调明亮；背景干净简洁，仅保留陶瓷碗与汤勺细节；画面整体呈现强烈治愈系、萌系风格，真实摄影质感与创意合成效果结合，高分辨率，细节清晰，构图紧凑，画面中心集中在汤勺中的宠物与周围汤圆，整体视觉统一。\",\"jV/DnQ\":\"Video\",\"m4SrIw\":\"Popular searches\",\"CZkHCw\":\"Video · {0}\",\"2F4txA\":\"A simple countdown timer\",\"AbbzZQ\":\"Catalan\",\"EdfTJQ\":\"Search graphics\",\"G0GXyg\":\"Congratulate my friend on their big achievement\",\"GbHgyA\":\"Describe what your chart styles convey and when to use them\",\"Y8Z05Q\":\"Undo\",\"dKJ+BA\":\"Lighting\",\"cvB9HA\":\"Generate voiceover\",\"VSnRyQ\":\"3D\",\"2nzn2g\":\"Search {0} layouts\",\"fcsxPA\":\"一锅汤圆汪（喵）\",\"+aAFyA\":\"<b>Deleting this section and its categories is permanent and cannot be undone.</b> For these categories, assets and guidelines will no longer be available, but any linked content may still be accessed elsewhere:\",\"rschNA\":\"Type\",\"nBkvDA\":\"You need to be online to use this app\",\"30ck2w\":\"Banner 2\",\"wFpnCQ\":\"Captions\",\"jnhQFQ\":\"To generate captions, you’ll need videos with speech placed on video or social media page types.\",\"0pS24g\":\"Template style\",\"lsDrAQ\":\"Upload\",\"Zmb3wA\":\"QR and barcodes\",\"MluUug\":\"Your request might result in something that doesn’t meet <a data-anchor-id=\\\"ai-policies-link\\\" href=\\\"#\\\">our policies</a>. If this doesn’t seem right, let us know.\",\"kt80FQ\":\"Romanian\",\"Fbdyig\":\"We couldn’t detect speech in your videos.\",\"iAOECQ\":\"Creating your captions\",\"druxSA\":\"Help me create a work r