\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\">{1}</a>.\",\"DIWgjQ\":\"Charts\",\"DOWnWw\":\"Create your chart styles\",\"kbbTrg\":\"Magic BG has finished generating\",\"3ebAnw\":\"Kannada\",\"94HCPw\":\"马年牛马本命照\",\"mI87EA\":\"Generate a hand-drawn illustration style workplace anxiety post on Xiaohongshu\",\"fl6rqA\":\"Draw, upload, or create your own signature to add to your documents.\",\"0t3Wqw\":\"Add common mistakes to avoid for charts\",\"24bFAQ\":\"Sound effects\",\"ZFhX9g\":\"Create an interactive memory matching game designed as a fun meeting ice breaker. Start with an example “Team Connect” game featuring 12 emoji cards (6 pairs), colourful workspace theme, and 10 conversation-starter questions ranging from “What emoji best describes your morning?” to “What’s a work skill you’re proud of developing?”\\n\\nAs a follow up ask me about: team/group size, preferred emoji categories, question themes (professional growth, personal interests, team dynamics), game customisation preferences (difficulty level, timer options)\",\"NNnsSQ\":\"Hearts\",\"N1090g\":\"There was a technical problem on our end. Try again later.\",\"q/bVDQ\":\"Select a font size\",\"uNRXeA\":\"Search keywords, tags, colour\",\"nXXNAw\":\"Folder added and shared\",\"i6NsBw\":\"sankey\",\"w0Fi5g\":\"Embed design\",\"qvQhJg\":\"Mockup\",\"B01+zA\":\"Data autofill\",\"YcvYPw\":\"Ask me anything\",\"nlRS0g\":\"Delete font style\",\"u5cbvg\":\"Style\",\"cQeqCg\":\"A document for remote work guidelines\",\"YDijzw\":\"I need a PPT for a product launch, focusing on highlighting product features and user value. The graphics should be modern and technological.\",\"CrNKVQ\":\"Start managing your content\",\"UeEodQ\":\"<strong>Address:</strong> {0}\",\"EjBR/Q\":\"with a point-of-view shot framing\",\"8h1xZg\":\"a postcard\",\"cbV3yA\":\"in a vector art style\",\"41qlhA\":\"Article\",\"vc6m8A\":\"Discard\",\"vzdqUQ\":\"Request access to these hidden folders to be able to <b>view</b> them in the Brand Kit and Projects.\",\"jpJLTA\":\"5-pointed star\",\"V1j8+w\":\"一个立体q版毛绒风格的元宝，造型圆润可爱，整体呈对称的元宝形，中间高高隆起，两侧自然下弯，整体仅有一种毛绒质感，以黄色为主，背景为暖红到米白的柔和渐变，氛围温馨喜庆、软萌吉祥。中心构图，四周留白，无文字\",\"HiJoiA\":\"See all\",\"XMe9Gw\":\"Marathi\",\"7QoMdA\":\"a story\",\"Jk1GCA\":\"Untitled\",\"LiuOeg\":\"Components aren’t supported in Responsive designs\",\"/EX50g\":\"Discard Changes\",\"6DmZcw\":\"an itinerary\",\"qV46Gw\":\"Breton\",\"vGYYfg\":\"Your changes will be instantly shared\",\"EJWHeg\":\"Bar chart\",\"bWg1zQ\":\"A presentation about investing for beginners\",\"13trbg\":\"Emoji\",\"OU7vjg\":\"No logos added\",\"ifuAHA\":\"Delete uploaded font?\",\"pAG2AQ\":\"Developer information\",\"kst8cg\":\"Circle\",\"6vU3tw\":\"Magic recommendations\",\"xPjHfw\":\"Ultra is for photos and videos only.\",\"pis4mA\":\"Shapes\",\"tX5vMA\":\"This app has updated permissions. To continue using it, please read and accept them.\",\"jZv2tA\":\"Create a closing scene for a nature documentary\",\"4zWlmA\":\"Minimalist flat illustration style, Girl wearing straw hat plays guitar, green clothes and black shoes , simple lines, bright colours, light blue background\",\"89XivA\":\"Upscale image\",\"KYm15w\":\"+1\",\"UTQ+QQ\":\"Could not save changes to Brand Kit. Please try again.\",\"Hrx8NA\":\"Students will take information about a provided historical event presented in textbook format and convert it into modern media formats like news reports, social media posts, and infographics for different audiences. This activity should develop students’s ability to represent the same historical information across multiple formats while maintaining accuracy and meaning.\",\"ZjAuJw\":\"with an over-the-shoulder shot framing\",\"JesfEg\":\"Create a marketing design featuring {0}\",\"pZG3bg\":\"Ads\",\"NOJ4gg\":\"新年招财主题Q版贴纸，画面居中单主体；必须使用参考图人物的真实照片人脸，保留真实皮肤纹理/毛孔/自然高光/真实摄影阴影，脸部清晰对焦，绝对禁止插画化/卡通化/3D化脸部；脸部为“照片贴纸拼贴”效果：真实人脸嵌入卡通头部，脸与卡通头部之间有轻微接触阴影与色温匹配，确保一眼看出“真实照片脸 + 刺绣卡通身体”。身体为Q版卡通财神娃娃，绒布刺绣/贴布绣工艺质感，金线绣纹+烫金压纹+亮粉金箔颗粒，粗描边+金色描边边框；头戴华丽新年冠冕；身穿红金配色中式财神袍；一只手向前指向镜头（透视适度不变形），另一只手举竖向红色卷轴/锦旗，卷轴为刺绣质感，金色中文字清晰可读“指定发财”。背景红粉渐变虚化+柔和节日散景粒子，画面干净无杂物，贴纸印刷质感，高清，边缘利落。\",\"HRjEDg\":\"Express your brand with fonts\",\"Wu0cww\":\"Your existing designs will be not affected if you delete the style.\",\"lb3uLg\":\"A white steed, composed as the horse’s upper body. Watercolor mixed-media in a warm, relaxed palette with rich colors, accented with specks of gold dust. A mysterious mood + a warm-toned wonderland + a bright background. Traditional Chinese layered mountains encircle the horse, with golden flowing clouds weaving through. Lively, expressive brushstrokes.\",\"v1tshA\":\"Grass green\",\"8NzenA\":\"Bug Life: Butterfly Metamorphosis\",\"1hpx9A\":\"Delete\",\"CeeRug\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any results for “{0}” in {1}. Try searching for something related or <a data-anchor-id=\\\"clear-expansion\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\">see all results for “{0}”</a>.\",\"5peREw\":\"Welsh\",\"oC7cvw\":\"Set up ready-to-use templates to make brand consistency even easier\",\"YnbL+g\":\"QR Code\",\"DpvaVw\":\"Print products\",\"9KOtsQ\":\"参考图中人物形象生成胶片写真，不要改变人物的五官，清透的伪素颜妆，以假乱真的伪素颜原生妆感，清晰的面部，淡淡的唇色。微仰拍视角，人物半蹲在地上看向镜头，特写人物脸部，夜晚天台，半身人像：人物穿着暗红色羊毛大衣，内搭浅色高领针织，微笑直视镜头；双手各持仙女棒，一根仙女棒靠近镜头前景爆闪形成强光斑与炫光，另一根在胸前闪烁。背景深色夜空与城市灯光散景，冷蓝环境光+暖橙火花强烈冷暖对比；人物清晰对焦、浅景深、手持抓拍感、胶片细颗粒。背景仅有远处淡淡烟花散点和尾迹，低饱和低亮度、强虚化、被烟雾遮挡，不影响人物主体。\",\"iwHcEQ\":\"Digital\",\"Pwb0lg\":\"To generate captions, you need to add media with speech to your design first.\",\"/EK6ng\":\"Import your media\",\"U9dO6Q\":\"Grids\",\"+NocHA\":\"Create an image of a plane taking off the runway with a beautiful sunrise\",\"kJgokQ\":\"Delete lesson\",\"PkasIw\":\"Text Explorer: Hidden Meanings in Stories\",\"L4WpLQ\":\"保持上图动物形象不变，生成一张写实风格的喜庆主题宠物写真，头戴可爱猪头帽，正对镜头站立，双爪抬起并抓住一条红色横幅，爪子自然搭在横幅上方，姿态端正又带点呆萌。眼睛微微睁大，表情无辜认真，红色横幅上有大字“和平年代适合养猪”，背景为纯红色喜庆背景，带有细腻的金色粉尘/金粉颗粒效果，营造节日祝福的氛围。\",\"pxHyPg\":\"Guidelines\",\"QX9ZDg\":\"Style\",\"fXM3aA\":\"Looks like something went wrong. Try again?\",\"COHQMQ\":\"Heading type\",\"8IUCOQ\":\"Dreamcore Chinese Girl with Horse\",\"a9gniA\":\"A grainy photo of a cat\",\"6QWMtw\":\"Failed to rename ingredient\",\"TFaWkg\":\"Stickers\",\"1drp5A\":\"Design business card copy for a photographer specializing in outdoor travel and humanities documentary\",\"gF3Wsw\":\"Create an esthetic happy birthday video\",\"VKHcvQ\":\"Design\",\"s5/feg\":\"Upload video when you’re back online.\",\"/kL1gQ\":\"Generate a lifestyle post suitable for “healing daily life” theme on Xiaohongshu\",\"N/ZYDA\":\"Pentagon\",\"ICjAZA\":\"Cartoon\",\"5Skn4A\":\"Posts designs to a specific channel at a chosen time.\",\"sdY0zw\":\"Grids\",\"lRshKA\":\"Unstarred\",\"qcT62Q\":\"a press release\",\"cFSTuQ\":\"Project management\",\"4cBDeQ\":\"Advocate for a cause\",\"2NGRKw\":\"Save your Brand Kit changes?\",\"Mae7Ww\":\"Request access to duplicate folders in the Brand Kit\",\"95UtFQ\":\"马脸高定\",\"reWqUQ\":\"Swedish\",\"o0YSqg\":\"Chinese Trend Style Soaring Dragon Illustration\",\"wGkJtQ\":\"<strong>These results have been restricted by your administrator.</strong><br/>Contact them to learn more, or try searching for something else.\",\"LvSTBQ\":\"Upload to {0}\",\"zQLurA\":\"Share\",\"9N3XiA\":\"Generate AI voice\",\"oH4I5Q\":\"Upload\",\"OA3jDA\":\"Vertical hexagon\",\"qGFvzQ\":\"Upload files\",\"lrUPeQ\":\"Add a subtitle\",\"7CkEYQ\":\"Add this to the canvas\",\"3XWLyA\":\"Ask the creator to add the right logos so everyone can use them with confidence.\",\"Dt9bpA\":\"Font\",\"SWFUKA\":\"Parallelogram right\",\"WbWdQg\":\"Rectangle\",\"LVDlkA\":\"Frosted Glass Texture 3D Folder Icon\",\"oztiDw\":\"Search types\",\"Bt+6Kw\":\"Display\",\"O/8rzA\":\"All selected ({0, number} of {0, plural, one {# suitable} other {# suitable}})\",\"ZCqJGA\":\"Woodcut engraving style with simple, bold lines. A hand is grabbing a horse’s head; the horse has an expression of rolling its eyes. Traditional Chinese New Year picture style, flat and cute, with a whimsical feel.\",\"bXoNNQ\":\"Arrow block right 2\",\"ce28Cg\":\"Delete {0} font style?\",\"I1Y8dQ\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any results for “{0}”. <a data-anchor-id=\\\"searchSuggestedQuery\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\">Search again in {2}</a> or try searching something related.\",\"64FaKg\":\"Arch up\",\"yFx7IA\":\"Tracks or automates tasks.\",\"AP+WZw\":\"Create a video of a high-altitude drone shot directly overhead, revealing a vast pine forest arranged in mesmerising radial symmetry. The treetops form tight concentric patterns, creating a fractal-like design of deep greens interspersed with golden tips. The frame is static, emphasising the sheer density and visual rhythm of nature’s geometry. This contemplative, aerial composition evokes order and infinity — stylised with natural colour grading and hyper-detailed forestry texture, perfect for abstract environmental cinematography.\",\"hpSyFA\":\"Tajik\",\"Bsn/aQ\":\"New\",\"cmePRQ\":\"3D art\",\"u0U3MA\":\"Drop in grids, circuits, and data-inspired shapes for a techy feel\",\"bSz8UQ\":\"Ask an admin to add templates so you can start with this brand’s assets and layouts ready.\",\"mk1RGA\":\"Press Release\",\"wu/HnA\":\"Be instantly recognisable with logos\",\"vvJpTA\":\"Kazakh\",\"iXJJ7w\":\"Art Stories: How Culture is Expressed\",\"fJgR4A\":\"Close Colours Menu\",\"f9keZw\":\"Software & technology\",\"LLEwYg\":\"Search combinations\",\"avXdZw\":\"Czech\",\"VNgD4Q\":\"保持上图形象不变，不要改变人物的五官，开心的表情，正面站立，萌娃抬头看向镜头，微俯拍视角，站在走廊里，人物戴鎏金帝王冠（红宝石、流苏），穿红底金纹财神华服（瑞兽、祥云），双手抱一个大金元宝；半身构图特写腰部以上，鱼眼超广角视角，轻微畸变，暗角效果，正中对称构图；红金配色，室内氛围，氛围喜庆可爱。室内暖色氛围，人物背后是一面墙（米色/浅棕墙面），顶部有暖黄色灯光光斑与柔和虚化；地面为浅色瓷砖，远处暖黄色顶灯/壁灯形成柔和光斑与虚化。\",\"xUAnJQ\":\"parliament chart\",\"Qaq6uA\":\"Spoken language\",\"fzYjqQ\":\"Casual\",\"EqD08w\":\"Suggest creative exercises to get unstuck\",\"UzOmew\":\"All results for “{0}”\",\"251A6g\":\"Add Custom\",\"tLivvA\":\"Pinterest Pin\",\"PryqJw\":\"Video\",\"JMsvCA\":\"Rename\",\"JmrECg\":\"Tell me what you’d like to design together...\",\"PjouPg\":\"Get help with this app\",\"q+9oWQ\":\"Search Elements Pro\",\"nag8DA\":\"Add this layout to the canvas\",\"WhTSAw\":\"Create an image of {0} {1}\",\"6DWnCQ\":\"Component source restored\",\"U88UNg\":\"<b>This audio is protected by copyright.</b> You can’t share or download it unless you have the rights. <a href=\\\"https://www.canva.com/help/audio-copyright-ownership/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Learn more</a>\",\"euGIjw\":\"Sanskrit\",\"qj3K7A\":\"Record yourself\",\"HuxVSg\":\"Request access\",\"j/VshA\":\"Search millions of photos\",\"9eQ16w\":\"Toasting marshmallows around a campfire\",\"4kUB1Q\":\"Polish\",\"WcqvgQ\":\"Upgrade to add chart styles\",\"HZCMDw\":\"Octagon\",\"BaU7eg\":\"Minimalist\",\"iwQgSQ\":\"Drop items to upload\",\"gF0PUQ\":\"Search fonts and combinations\",\"fe8BWw\":\"Upload folder\",\"pkxgHA\":\"Provides a library of custom icons and illustrations or generates them using AI.\",\"A9IIBQ\":\"Graphics\",\"z9jEMQ\":\"Creates customizable frames for photos, graphics, or videos.\",\"REqfZg\":\"The centre is Skin care products, placed on a piece of wood in the shape of a log sculpture, with Green plants and magnolia flowers Decorate with half a avocado, minimalist art style photography, with a light yellow background and obvious light and shadow.\",\"a+pAdA\":\"Explore the set\",\"Ou8oSw\":\"Turn your media into a polished video — just upload, describe your story, and we’ll handle the edit.\",\"3YzDZw\":\"年画娃娃\",\"jeONTw\":\"Choose a language\",\"34YvKg\":\"Consumer packaged goods\",\"7tj4Wg\":\"No Brand Templates added\",\"FbmlHA\":\"Scrapbook\",\"kff6PA\":\"3. Select <strong>Create component</strong>.\",\"H4BOEA\":\"See similar tracks\",\"Ppdf5A\":\"Regenerate all shapes\",\"FGwDLQ\":\"Open app\",\"RjMkqw\":\"Brand voice\",\"19YTQw\":\"Ask the creator to define your default fonts for a clear and consistent look.\",\"F47abg\":\"Search “{0}”\",\"38ioeg\":\"Search photos\",\"0lgXng\":\"No valid charts for your query.\",\"DkwtNQ\":\"Brand Templates\",\"a8UqtQ\":\"Twitter Post\",\"GndbJQ\":\"Logos you upload to your Brand Kit will appear here.\",\"/ySgKg\":\"Search backgrounds\",\"CHfQJw\":\"a business card\",\"3Xo14g\":\"Add your brand logos\",\"NgXvrg\":\"Styles can’t be used in Docs\",\"luZkEg\":\"Cancel\",\"RUoYkg\":\"dual axis\",\"ZL5djQ\":\"Japanese\",\"Bs4sew\":\"Done\",\"VuxbQg\":\"Search styles\",\"6RYKwQ\":\"保持上图动物形象不变，生成横向三宫格胶片质感艺术感写真图，场景为山脚下、天空、傍晚。图中动物形象保持不变。第一张为动物的上半身，露出动物的侧脸，眺望远山，添加中英字幕“跨过这道山，就是新的一年。 -Beyond this mountain lies a new year.-”；第二张为动物的大脸照，左脸有柔光，添加中英字幕“你以为我在感慨时光。-You think I’m lost in thoughts of time.-”；第三张为动物伟岸的背影，背影可以再胖一点，远处放一个小山进行对比，天空中有漫天烟花，添加中英字幕“其实我只是，胖得跳不动了。-Actually, I’m just too fat to jump anymore.-”。整体色调温暖，带有富士胶片效果，低对比度，暗部细节保留完整，高光区域呈现自然晕化、均采用柔和漫射光，无明显硬边阴影，营造出文艺的氛围，三张图合成一个三宫格，字幕位于底部居中。图片比例3:4。\",\"cev50g\":\"Collaborating with a team\",\"SLgB3A\":\"Choose colour\",\"FoIS7w\":\"Create an interactive colour accessibility simulator. Start with an example featuring a primary colour palette (#3366CC blue, #FF9900 orange, #66CC33 green) shown across different vision impairments (deuteranopia, protanopia, tritanopia) with WCAG compliance indicators and alternative suggestions.\\n\\nAs a follow up ask me about: specific colours to test, vision conditions to prioritise, desired accessibility compliance level (AA or AAA), additional features (export options, colour palette generation)\",\"LIHEhw\":\"App\",\"01RD7g\":\"Funny Horse\",\"LpEGBA\":\"Templates\",\"TCuN7w\":\"Malagasy\",\"9kHVfA\":\"(Optional)\",\"oIc1kw\":\"Text generators\",\"ANRD8A\":\"Website\",\"WpELFA\":\"Describe what you are after and attach media.\",\"WV1VFw\":\"Apply style to page\",\"biYstA\":\"Quick add\",\"1xkVJQ\":\"We’ll choose the best length\",\"qr9BYg\":\"Charts\",\"cMCJBQ\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any backgrounds.\",\"Us7VJQ\":\"Edit photos with BadTV’s old-school effects\",\"KWZksQ\":\"in a stock photo style\",\"tBL3Dg\":\"Add this line to the canvas\",\"kR3B9g\":\"Set a custom name for this font style\",\"e03ULg\":\"Sound Effects\",\"jzN1qw\":