\"zx1/nA\":\"Apply\",\"CbtqbA\":\"Open template item page\",\"g2Uqvg\":\"Other apps\",\"eKSRrw\":\"Literary handwriting font “Life is long and has its own answers”, cleverly connected, flexible and jumping, staggered, some strokes extended, white characters, frosted texture blue and white cloud sky background\",\"PKpFjA\":\"Content\",\"KosvUw\":\"Save changes\",\"rLaivw\":\"Looks like something went wrong. Try again?\",\"EaiwLg\":\"View collection\",\"IcpxjA\":\"Asset category\",\"F+hupA\":\"Get help with Brand Kit setup\",\"vVChrw\":\"Removed for Offline\",\"gznJRQ\":\"Design, checks, or publishes digital ads.\",\"nLB8Rw\":\"Hero image\",\"2YBLIw\":\"Delete\",\"xTTTFw\":\"Black\",\"XwKVnQ\":\"To generate captions, you need to add videos with speech to your design first.\",\"98UUHQ\":\"This Brand Kit has unsaved fonts\",\"+DDKhQ\":\"Text added\",\"1+uYEQ\":\"Thanks for your feedback.\",\"4zmBAg\":\"You have reached the limit of {0} uploads for this brand ingredient\",\"K2VTMg\":\"Generating captions is taking longer than expected.\",\"SoyLsw\":\"To caption audio, convert page to video and enter timeline view.\",\"JWRMzQ\":\"Elegant\",\"CZ5p2Q\":\"Code\",\"sdW8lg\":\"Stay on brand, your way\",\"znPSAA\":\"Icons and illustrations\",\"jb3sgg\":\"Shona\",\"hUZhEQ\":\"Apply both pages\",\"Sq5/Mw\":\"参考图中的人物形象生成马头人身拟人形象，只参考图中人物发型、配饰、服装；坐在办公室工位上，对着电脑举哑铃；创意噪点摄影，胶片质感，慢快门动态残影，整体晃朦，褪色，轻微过曝，画面严重模糊，充满杂色颗粒，主体仅显轮廓、细节模糊，低饱和度\",\"u+pRoQ\":\"Charts\",\"Avs0pQ\":\"Search results for “{0}”\",\"ymqgVA\":\"Remove from category\",\"DvFLJg\":\"Follow any setup steps in the Canva editor if the app requires it.\",\"IvZRhQ\":\"Faroese\",\"K/g5HQ\":\"Style for this brand template is unavailable. Please try another template.\",\"8QFF7A\":\"Brand Kit isn’t set up yet\",\"Vo7fNg\":\"in a 16:9 aspect ratio\",\"KR/4ww\":\"Trending apps\",\"kC3PvQ\":\"Video files are unsupported for this page\",\"ksQiKg\":\"Browse frames\",\"JETNgg\":\"Generate background, text, and element colours to use them in one step.\",\"yETOpQ\":\"See all\",\"gOzxYw\":\"Speech bubble\",\"/cHnRg\":\"What type of imagery would suit my project\",\"SFsW1Q\":\"Delete guidelines\",\"qAi4NA\":\"Soft lighting\",\"Kh1VZA\":\"in a surreal / dreamlike style\",\"zZYwow\":\"Keep\",\"TSbSpQ\":\"Cancel\",\"ei1fMw\":\"A journal entry from your future self in 10 years\",\"lqtofQ\":\"Craft the right words, then transform them with eye-catching effects, colours, and fonts.\",\"5rj3tg\":\"Doc\",\"OD3eIQ\":\"Tap text to add to page\",\"vWXwAg\":\"Business\",\"J5N2aQ\":\"Macedonian\",\"nY3Z6g\":\"Create an animated loading screen of a cat\",\"zgn7KQ\":\"Create an interactive historical timeline component that engages students. Start with an example “Ancient Civilisations” timeline (3000 BCE-500 CE) featuring Egyptian, Greek, and Roman key events with expandable information cards and a cohesive visual style.\\n\\nAs a follow up ask me about: specific historical events/period to include, student age group, theme focus (cultural, scientific, political), visual style preferences, interactive element preferences\",\"nzp64A\":\"This video is not supported.\",\"V9UkLw\":\"Bullet point {0}: “{1}” {2}/{3} characters\",\"tT1Jfw\":\"Dismiss\",\"AC6oMQ\":\"No audio\",\"z0O0ZQ\":\"Homepage\",\"UmC+sQ\":\"Organic\",\"mk7Q0A\":\"Failed to reorder\",\"/cmvuQ\":\"Apply colours only\",\"t2rauA\":\"<strong>Phone:</strong> {0}\",\"gzQLWw\":\"A city skyline at dusk\",\"KknKfA\":\"Browse photos\",\"f/xnKQ\":\"Add asset category\",\"DhFh6Q\":\"More options\",\"lDKCWw\":\"Students will design innovative solutions for erosion control, considering environmental impact, cost-effectiveness, and long-term sustainability. This activity should integrate knowledge of earth science, engineering principles, and environmental stewardship while encouraging creative problem-solving.\",\"XD+doA\":\"Remove\",\"eLMTmQ\":\"Create an Image of toasting marshmallows around a campfire with the campfire in focus\",\"pbINHQ\":\"Finnish\",\"ty9EXA\":\"Canva is having trouble disconnecting this app. Check your connection or try again later.\",\"Nrcvug\":\"Aspect Ratio\",\"mG4xgQ\":\"Select voice\",\"SLJIoQ\":\"A new Chinese wedding invitation copy, theme within 8 words\",\"D3p6FQ\":\"Chinese (Cantonese, Hong Kong)\",\"d5V5Ww\":\"Text only\",\"OHyJVg\":\"Pixel art\",\"PLw2Sw\":\"Ink Wash Horse\",\"UHkdIw\":\"Captions\",\"faJk5g\":\"Provided by <a data-anchor-id=\\\"creator\\\" href=\\\"#\\\">{0}</a>\",\"E2uWUg\":\"Highest quality, great for images and video. Upgrade for more.\",\"HlrKQw\":\"Peach\",\"WVtsFg\":\"Canva design\",\"d/jxCQ\":\"Generate shapes\",\"QIkqVA\":\"A colour accessibility simulator\",\"70smrA\":\"App is targeted at Enterprise users only\",\"iUmNUA\":\"Find other Brand Templates under your Projects or ask your admin to set them up in this folder.\",\"GaKJKQ\":\"Video effects\",\"b15jyw\":\"Add logos\",\"cT2DOQ\":\"Your team apps\",\"nPVmfw\":\"with a bokeh effect\",\"J/hESw\":\"Design a promotional instagram post featuring a bottle of natural, organic skincare. Showcase its eco-friendly packaging, key ingredients, and a fresh, earthy esthetic.\",\"KDGrbw\":\"Hindi\",\"vmE1dQ\":\"No brand assets added yet\",\"BWU6HQ\":\"Link\",\"iQetiA\":\"Top-down shot\",\"j8Mmow\":\"<a data-anchor-id=\\\"searchOriginalQuery\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\">Search again in {1}</a>.\",\"qNCMCg\":\"in a macro photography style\",\"H3BZAQ\":\"Personalise any design with Google Analytics data\",\"Fxxnzw\":\"Sindhi\",\"yTOETQ\":\"To generate captions, you’ll need media with speech placed on video or social media page types.\",\"1rAITA\":\"Add a voice to reflect your brand personality\",\"Nn3bnA\":\"survey chart\",\"kGZA+Q\":\"Create a poster on {0}\",\"wLipiQ\":\"Premium\",\"o+nf8g\":\"This style can’t be applied to this document.\",\"L7mreg\":\"Chinese classical architecture, the palace has a corner tower, a golden roof, and exquisite eaves. The building stands on a high red palace wall with white stone railings. The sky has a soft gradient and the tones are simple and elegant.\",\"ot9eiA\":\"Uzbek\",\"fFRWOA\":\"Vertical\",\"UU8ePg\":\"Round squares\",\"LLuEkQ\":\"<strong>Developer:</strong> {0}\",\"VCPnKg\":\"Apply colours to all pages\",\"WYqrWg\":\"Cartoon Hand-drawn Style Bunny Snowman Illustration\",\"l5v7gQ\":\"Make a killer presentation\",\"5wJTRw\":\"Length\",\"PJ0dpg\":\"Add to page\",\"BbheKA\":\"Mockups\",\"aMiQpw\":\"Palettes have not been set\",\"0QSCgg\":\"RED Note Post\",\"erTTiQ\":\"Design an instagram post to Celebrate World Design Day\",\"E+cbLw\":\"If they doubted you, they’re about to be fans.\",\"CKZAOQ\":\"{0} deleted\",\"G+qIvw\":\"Tables\",\"2/Dytw\":\"Copyright protected\",\"FChrHg\":\"Banner Landscape\",\"ODD5kQ\":\"Add Brand Templates\",\"ckocDQ\":\"A review of a book series you recently discovered\",\"sy9YsA\":\"Students will research breakthrough medical treatments and explain how these innovations are transforming healthcare and patient outcomes. This activity should connect scientific research to real-world applications and help students understand the process of medical innovation.\",\"CMtRew\":\"with a duration of 8 seconds\",\"4dPCnA\":\"Designs\",\"zdzqhw\":\"Images\",\"6ifLPQ\":\"I need help creating a complete brand launch campaign for a new business. I want you to act as my senior brand designer and guide me through this step-by-step. Before we start designing anything, please ask me 3 focused questions selected from this list, one at a time to understand: 1. What type of business and industry this is 2. What makes this business unique 3. Launch timeline and priority channels 4. Who the target audience is 5. Visual and verbal style preferences You MUST start your first response with a brief, professional introduction then move directly to the first question. Don’t use casual language like “Alright” or “Let’s dive right in!” - keep it professional and focused. Ask the questions one at a time and provide contextual suggestions when helpful based on previous answers. Please limit yourself to three questions and then you should recommend creating a design using the information (e.g. “Should I create an X for you now?”). Start with the most important question first. Keep your tone conversational, friendly, and professional - like a trusted creative partner, not robotic. Only add explanations for questions if it’s not obvious why that information would be needed. Guidelines for design outputs Clarity first: every asset must communicate the brand’s core promise at a glance. Audience alignment: visuals and voice should mirror the audience’s aspirations. Visual hierarchy: guide the eye; spotlight key messages. Cross-channel agility: design for effortless adaptation across social, email, and web. Consistency: use consistent colours, typography, and tone throughout.\",\"3swnqg\":\"百宝箱变出财神宠物\",\"YVlzcw\":\"Communication\",\"chZscQ\":\"This image cannot be added to your design.\",\"pKcO7A\":\"Line art\",\"p5FzkQ\":\"A plane taking off the runway with a beautiful sunrise\",\"4uQMeQ\":\"Create on brand quickly with components\",\"xRIj8g\":\"Mockups\",\"d/PpTQ\":\"Delete the category, {0}?\",\"Pqgj6w\":\"Stock Photo\",\"FxzpIA\":\"Create a single shot ad for a vintage fashion label\",\"Qn6SPA\":\"Too many assets in this category. Delete some to upload.\",\"918Vww\":\"Add this quiz to the canvas\",\"BhR9sA\":\"a speech\",\"ecVd0w\":\"Generating decorations that match your page. You can continue editing other pages in the meantime.\",\"11Vacg\":\"Decide for me\",\"wA85Xw\":\"Feedback submitted. Thank you!\",\"JVcatQ\":\"We couldn’t load the style for this brand template. Please try again later.\",\"vkledw\":\"AI text\",\"wjxrDg\":\"参考图中的人物形象生成马头人身拟人形象，参考图中人物发型、服装；马头人坐在现代开放式办公室的工位上自拍，脖子上挂着带有工作证件的深蓝色挂绳，工作证件/工牌上是马头人身的西装照。正用吸管喝着透明塑料杯里的冰美式咖啡，桌上放着黑色键盘。背景是忙碌的办公场景，有模糊的同事和办公隔间。写实摄影风格，光线明亮均匀，细节丰富，整体呈现出幽默的职场日常氛围。\",\"sNdjOA\":\"Apply “{0}” style\",\"ZBvBzw\":\"a script\",\"StANyA\":\"Photos\",\"azJG8Q\":\"{0, plural, one {# Item} other {# Items}}\",\"8og6nw\":\"Learning activity\",\"p4aHiQ\":\"Add a scrollable animation to your doc\",\"39cxJw\":\"in an elegant style\",\"nHYsRw\":\"Thanks for your feedback.\",\"UMH8Nw\":\"Subtitles\",\"aAZTeQ\":\"Upload\",\"N+I/fg\":\"AI audio\",\"xav3hQ\":\"No apps currently in use\",\"pPsgLQ\":\"<b>Applying styles is not yet available between these page types.</b> Select another page type, then try again.\",\"uDYSLA\":\"You’ve reached your voiceover limit. Try again tomorrow.\",\"JQdvPg\":\"Design a cover image for my travel vlog in Tokyo\",\"3bUzug\":\"Text added\",\"TslZWQ\":\"Videos\",\"VOHYVg\":\"See all\",\"ALfuYA\":\"Generate from photo\",\"33pxwg\":\"Create a sketch of a cat playing with a ball of yellow yarn\",\"Cd6f2Q\":\"Music is ready\",\"5suCcg\":\"avatar generation\",\"M90Cyg\":\"Sketch - Black & White\",\"wN2jpw\":\"Marketing campaigns\",\"jJQm8w\":\"Chinese Style Rock Colour Year of Horse Illustration\",\"oQt7iQ\":\"3D\",\"OScJAQ\":\"Did you know the word “emoji” comes from Japanese and means “picture character”?\",\"E7/q+Q\":\"Add common mistakes to avoid for colours\",\"yoQIag\":\"新年主题写真人像，不要改变人物的五官，清晰的面部，穿浅色针织开衫，搭配红色围巾，戴着红色的毛线手套；人物居中近景半身像，双手各举一个橙子贴在脸颊两侧，微笑直视镜头；温暖的早晨室外年味场景：奶油色墙面与木质门廊/窗框，旁边挂一串红灯笼与流苏中国结，地面或角落摆放一盆金桔树/年桔盆栽与几只红色红包点缀；背景远处有暖黄小串灯形成散景光点；画面加入少量金色亮片/金粉微粒在空气中漂浮，明亮均匀、肤质真实有纹理，高清细节，轻微浅景深，真实摄影质感，喜庆的氛围。\",\"tkgKKg\":\"Your team administrator has restricted access to this app. Please contact them to get access.\",\"0roJug\":\"Hide\",\"s+w2yA\":\"Background\",\"z5Drug\":\"Add new\",\"Klu1cg\":\"Recording Studio is unavailable right now. Try again soon.\",\"TVXMCQ\":\"I understand the deletion of this section and its categories cannot be undone.\",\"0oH43w\":\"Most popular\",\"ccoscA\":\"Thai\",\"/9hmFQ\":\"Lincoln’s Words: Hidden Power of the Gettysburg Address\",\"9Pq2aQ\":\"Image\",\"7k4nMQ\":\"Component deleted\",\"efyM/Q\":\"New\",\"UYCLcw\":\"Describe your background idea\",\"AKcX9w\":\"Something went wrong with {0}. Please try again later.\",\"Pze