a cinematic video of an ethereal, glass feather\",\"uokRKA\":\"Mixed-media\",\"gmdnQg\":\"Pop Art\",\"qsqTew\":\"E.g. tropical island sunset, watercolour style\",\"mLKD/w\":\"Lithuanian\",\"hTcDCQ\":\"Add page(s)\",\"NuhS/A\":\"Select video\",\"k5oYyA\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any {0, select, photos {photos} graphics {graphics} videos {videos} audio {audio} other {results}} for “{1}”. Try searching for something related or <a data-anchor-id=\\\"clear-filters\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\">clear filters</a>.\",\"7wmKCg\":\"Apply style only\",\"87lb/g\":\"Bulgarian\",\"jCB2Zg\":\"Teaching Plan\",\"i1CppA\":\"Close\",\"0868iw\":\"Table\",\"sVZM0A\":\"This folder is empty\",\"oCGy0A\":\"Selected {0, plural, one {# time} other {# times}}.\",\"pTprDA\":\"Crosses\",\"K/QVRA\":\"Hawaiian\",\"Ai3bwQ\":\"Pro\",\"R1Scqw\":\"Add a custom palette\",\"B2d6TA\":\"Itinerary\",\"5e+j2g\":\"Describe what your logos represents and when to use them\",\"KO8KZw\":\"Deleting this section is permanent and cannot be undone.\",\"lB2FBg\":\"No brand fonts set up yet\",\"CnUj7g\":\"No assets added\",\"+jxVdA\":\"Input Prompt\",\"k2qCVA\":\"Card\",\"X/a+1Q\":\"Add fonts\",\"F7iBPw\":\"App is targeted at Pro, Business and Enterprise users\",\"ybC/Eg\":\"Ask your admin to define your default fonts for a clear and consistent look.\",\"tp5dbg\":\"Images\",\"AMBiCg\":\"Description\",\"Fjxdgw\":\"You can still access elements that are available offline.\",\"ETp+Mg\":\"See all Audio\",\"SDAqPg\":\"in a VHS style\",\"tUvjMQ\":\"5 - Exceptional\",\"GXsxlA\":\"interactive content\",\"KG/sgA\":\"in an animated style\",\"rZNAXA\":\"Maltese\",\"cGMNjw\":\"Project Proposal\",\"FEVixA\":\"Generates unique, scannable QR or barcodes.\",\"vQsXrw\":\"Browse elements\",\"TjIK2w\":\"Dismiss magic recommendations\",\"mjuhHA\":\"Are you sure you want to delete this section?\",\"AYJttw\":\"Duration\",\"F/hZxw\":\"Cancel\",\"D5Ktbg\":\"Colours\",\"+0lE0g\":\"Sorry, we couldn’t find any images for “{0}”. Try searching something related.\",\"HIOcWA\":\"Playful\",\"r0tQrw\":\"Healthcare\",\"ga6OPQ\":\"a video script\",\"20bUdA\":\"Add asset category\",\"XXnzpw\":\"A copywriting for the details page of an invisible waist support waist protector for “office sedentary people”\",\"aZff/w\":\"Share\",\"5F6vHQ\":\"Flipbooks\",\"mvChSw\":\"in a vibrant style\",\"F7ebeg\":\"Purple\",\"yLGflg\":\"By using this app, you agree to its <terms-link>Terms &amp; Conditions and Privacy Policy</terms-link>.\",\"Gi7aqA\":\"Page {0}\",\"HOZLew\":\"Put some neon accents and electric shapes for a bold look\",\"y9L9eQ\":\"Cantonese\",\"miJRgg\":\"Arrow down\",\"oJ8D5g\":\"Make designs shine with ready-made icons, illustrations, patterns, and more.\",\"UP6yeg\":\"a Pinterest pin\",\"xEBl2A\":\"Apply style\",\"iQuGtg\":\"Planning events\",\"pm/P5A\":\"Connect with your network over email, instant message, and social media.\",\"iSyxOA\":\"You don’t have access to some folders in this Brand Kit, so they won’t be included in any duplicates you make.\",\"Kc1ajA\":\"Pro\",\"0WNPOA\":\"Video\",\"YnMHgA\":\"Recently used\",\"4W8ZnQ\":\"Styles, enhances, or manipulates video footage.\",\"BOjfdA\":\"Choose a font\",\"sof1rg\":\"Scatter halftone dots and textures for a retro, printed look\",\"8zM+Bg\":\"Design a minimalist logo for my creative design studio, “Borcelle”, emphasising the letter “B”.\",\"6d7o/g\":\"Share\",\"xk9Wsg\":\"Yes. Apps in the Canva Apps Marketplace are reviewed against Canva’s security requirements. You can see what {0} can access in its permissions.\",\"u6vzZw\":\"Your design doesn’t have any suitable media.\",\"RDpvRQ\":\"Data Connectors\",\"6bMsqg\":\"Screen recorder for desktop\",\"xQPZNQ\":\"Perfect for business cards, posters and more. Enter a URL and we’ll create a QR code for you to add to your designs.\",\"MMUcuA\":\"this\",\"PPQvIg\":\"Try our design school courses\",\"nRZRTw\":\"Templates\",\"q5JJrg\":\"Save\",\"OhomQw\":\"Uploads\",\"c5UTSw\":\"16:9\",\"6fwncw\":\"Shapes\",\"/dL8rA\":\"Share\",\"kn9R2g\":\"Elements\",\"IYyNng\":\"Data connectors\",\"2FRSEg\":\"Add\",\"c3RR/g\":\"A poster title for a forest therapy camp that advocates “unplugging on weekends”\",\"tQtY+w\":\"Sign up or log in to Canva.\",\"XFotag\":\"Summary\",\"QOA6kw\":\"Help me create a workplace work report PPT\",\"oSSyZw\":\"in a 3:4 aspect ratio\",\"Sni9/Q\":\"Magnificent Palace Complex Photography\",\"cmT/jQ\":\"Digital\",\"IJjt3g\":\"AI Voice\",\"9RkzVA\":\"with golden hour lighting\",\"XXUwtQ\":\"Mockups\",\"ru3EnA\":\"参考图中人物形象生成时尚大片风格的写实摄影，不要改变人物的五官，人物与一匹黑色马极近距离同框拍摄，马头体量巨大、真实比例，贴近镜头并占据画面重要位置，与人物在视觉上同等强度，马头遮挡人物半张脸，形成强烈对称与共生构图。 人物直视镜头，表情冷静克制。身着黑色立领极简风格服装，金属纽扣纵向排列，佩戴简约金色耳饰。发型与参考图一致，具有清晰可见的头发纹理与发丝细节。 场景为户外马场环境，白色围栏与自然背景虚化，自然柔光拍摄，低饱和冷色调，浅景深，焦点精准集中在人物眼睛与面部轮廓。 整体画面真实写实，细腻材质与光影控制，超高分辨率，国际一线时尚杂志封面级编辑摄影风格。\",\"5aHDwQ\":\"Folder shared with all Brand Kit users\",\"AeweSQ\":\"a letter\",\"i1lb2A\":\"Rename\",\"kpE1Hg\":\"Backgrounds are unavailable\",\"J2kMqw\":\"from <a data-anchor-id=\\\"open-brand-expansion\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\">{0}</a>\",\"b7i6PQ\":\"A delicious, healthy pasta dinner\",\"2CMtnA\":\"Videos\",\"p4McVw\":\"Click text to add to page\",\"G8Pweg\":\"Resume\",\"rG40Sw\":\"Create a RED Note on {0}\",\"YrajJg\":\"“You Look Interesting” Modern Font\",\"Nm6TYQ\":\"I need help creating a beautiful, on-brand event invitation that captures the right mood and includes all the essential details at a glance. I want you to act as my graphic designer specialising in event invitations. Before we start designing anything, please ask me 3 focused questions selected from this list, one at a time to understand: 1. Event type & purpose 2. Date, time & location 3. Delivery format (print, digital, or both) 4. Tone, formality, and theme 5. Visual preferences (colours, typography, vibe) You MUST ask the questions one at a time. Please ask no more than three questions and then you should recommend the best invitation design approach using the information (e.g. “Should I create X for you now?”). Start with the most important question first. Keep your tone warm and conversational - like a trusted creative partner who knows how to spotlight the who, what, when, and where with clear visual hierarchy. Make sure the design will be legible on both screens and print.I need help creating a beautiful, on-brand event invitation that captures the right mood and includes all the essential details at a glance. I want you to act as my graphic designer specialising in event invitations. Before we start designing anything, please ask me 3 focused questions selected from this list, one at a time to understand: 1. Event type & purpose 2. Date, time & location 3. Delivery format (print, digital, or both) 4. Tone, formality, and theme 5. Visual preferences (colours, typography, vibe) You MUST start your first response with a brief, professional introduction then move directly to the first question. Don’t use casual language like “Alright” or “Let’s dive right in!” - keep it professional and focused. Ask the questions one at a time and provide contextual suggestions when helpful based on previous answers. Please ask no more than three questions and then you should recommend creating an invitation using the information (e.g. “Should I create an X for you now?”). Start with the most important question first. Keep your tone warm and conversational - like a trusted creative partner who knows how to spotlight the who, what, when, and where with clear visual hierarchy. Make sure the design will be legible on both screens and print. Only add explanations for questions if it’s not obvious why that information would be needed. Guidelines for design outputs Clarity first: spotlight the who, what, when, and where. Tone match: mirror the event’s formality and theme. Visual hierarchy: let the eye land on event name, date/time, then RSVP. Balance & breathing room: keep the layout uncluttered. Legibility everywhere: ensure clear type on screens and printed stock. Consistency: stick to a unified palette, typography, and style throughout.\",\"oc5EsQ\":\"Arch down\",\"VqNYDg\":\"We could not upload some of your files because they aren’t supported in the Brand Kit. Please choose only <strong>{0}</strong> files to upload. Try uploading these files again once you save them in a different format\",\"ZlVxYw\":\"Arrow block right\",\"IPAZbA\":\"Videos\",\"cuS4EQ\":\"photo slider\",\"MdsWPA\":\"Close-up shot\",\"2IDMXw\":\"Starred for team\",\"5m0b7w\":\"Dynamic\",\"1tUZog\":\"Brand Template style\",\"UQDLsw\":\"New\",\"lxTprw\":\"Tracks from our popular music library aren’t available in your country yet.\",\"HUotyQ\":\"Premium (default)\",\"R3bRAw\":\"Design a presentation about investing for beginners\",\"VdzeDg\":\"Add common mistakes to avoid for logos\",\"TtXdKw\":\"After you’re done with this design, you can turn it into a reusable template.\",\"6cjdtw\":\"Designs are ready\",\"MMgAlw\":\"Your Story\",\"x5Py8Q\":\"Generate colour theme\",\"Vk8/1Q\":\"Search charts from Canva\",\"2RM/hg\":\"Search input to filter Brand Templates\",\"HiEPJw\":\"Developer resources\",\"X+vtzw\":\"Instagram Post\",\"yPB3jA\":\"Find Canva wherever you are in Google Workspace\",\"Vn9thg\":\"Unlink from logos\",\"EyAQcw\":\"Tagalog\",\"tO00aw\":\"Standard is for photos only.\",\"lNKvjA\":\"Remove from Brand Kit\",\"+rms5Q\":\"Apply captions to\",\"pkQjAA\":\"Other\",\"zgUkxg\":\"Trending apps\",\"x3HtOg\":\"Add chart styles for branded communications\",\"iFJFHA\":\"Delete\",\"zoUepg\":\"Hungarian\",\"cJYO+A\":\"Malayalam\",\"NMvBDQ\":\"New\",\"e7PNbA\":\"Instagram Post\",\"QTficQ\":\"Cancel\",\"o/HmxA\":\"Doc\",\"Rzvf6A\":\"Error: result could not be displayed\",\"3mhQSA\":\"{0} {0, plural, one {folder} other {folders}}\",\"CyQmhA\":\"Make available offline\",\"hDXAZg\":\"Link copied to clipboard\",\"k1G9SQ\":\"Draft a business roadmap for a tech startup’s first year\",\"7m1pQg\":\"Oriental woman in Hanfu Sitting beside a bush of flowers. The background is a classical Chinese painting depicting a magnolia tree in full bloom. The overall atmosphere is tranquil and elegant, with soft light and shadow.\",\"/ml+Dg\":\"Apply all {0, plural, one {# section} other {# sections}}\",\"yLa/SQ\":\"Add general guidelines…\",\"8X4X1A\":\"Components aren’t supported in docs right now.\",\"rglZ9w\":\"Upload Error\",\"Eg2mZw\":\"German\",\"gtDpOg\":\"Ask the creator to define your colour palettes to help you stay consistent and save time across designs.\",\"DQWNKA\":\"Add Page\",\"B+Zg4Q\":\"Skip Personalisation\",\"ZwaomQ\":\"An interactive pricing calculator that I can share with my clients\",\"AGJHpg\":\"Add a new asset category\",\"BuXAzw\":\"Draft a Canva doc in the format of {1} about {0}\",\"RnJ0Kw\":\"Create something new\",\"z+M1xg\":\"A blog documenting a 30-day fitness challenge\",\"gKMSUQ\":\"你是脱脂牛马吗\",\"TbTHvA\":\"No apps found\",\"oKNGvw\":\"You’ve used all your free storage. Upgrade to {0} or delete files from Uploads.\",\"6WMuAQ\":\"Punjabi\",\"b0u/uw\":\"Showing videos that are free for you\",\"iXeLsg\":\"Your design doesn’t have any suitable videos.\",\"6HuTEQ\":\"Featured apps\",\"yvWvpQ\":\"Do\",\"WAhHVg\":\"Create a design\",\"4MYVkg\":\"参考图中人物形象生成写实摄影风格的新年主题写真，不要改变人物的五官，不要有发饰，表情开心嘟嘴，身穿红色针织毛衣，质感柔软细腻，人物正对镜头，双手拿“福”字门贴，靠近脸部，搞怪可爱，背景为室内镜面场景，人物背后有一面镜子，镜中清晰反射出人物的侧后方轮廓与红色毛衣，形成前后呼应的构图。镜面上可见口红手写风格的新年装饰元素：“2026 马上发财”字样与简单笑脸涂鸦，构图为中近景人像，人物居中略偏右，背景虚化适度，不喧宾夺主。光线为柔和室内暖光，均匀照亮面部，肤质细腻真实，无过度磨皮。\",\"zqZrJA\":\"Search when you’re back online\",\"X55NIg\":\"Design a card for my friend congratulating them on their big achievement, using vibrant colours and an image of a person throwing confetti.\",\"4nhIAg\":\"Describe what you are after to get started\",\"cTJSrQ\":\"To use the captions feature, add media to a video or social media page type.\",\"0YMPNA\":\"Add to Brand Kit\",\"5H42cg\":\"File import and export\",\"G9fucA\":\"Beautify has finished generating\",\"ngIhAw\":\"Untitled component\",\"uVZvlQ\":\"Animation\",\"pPK9tA\":\"Play around with Canva\",\"g0qq/Q\":\"Create a social media post featuring {0} {1}\",\"mFM9FQ\":\"Decorate has finished generating\",\"091irA\":\"Cross\",\"aStOvg\":\"Charts\",\"68cMIw\":\"AI voice added to timeline\",\"GNynbA\":\"Learn more\",\"6WJlug\":\"Styles can’t be used in Code pages\",\"/aqWrQ\":\"Select media\",\"6+ILHw\":\"Start with an example\",\"MkjtSA\":\"Arrow vertical\",\"mvVIeQ\":\"Generates documents, like CVs, books, or worksheets, using AI.\",\"qGrx0g\":\"Want the best quality results?\",\"9xhK4A\":\"No brand voice added\",\"loJP0g\":\"Set up Brand Templates for this folder\",\"RBJfMw\":\"Make copies, edit the source (source of truth), then select <strong>Change all</strong> to update every copy.\",\"GCJ4+g\":\"word cloud\",\"1WqA5Q\":\"Describe what your graphics convey and when to use them\",\"Br0ebg\":\"Glowing blue Folder Suspended on a three-dimensional circular platform, it features transparent materials and light effect details. The overall design is simple and modern, with smooth lines and a predominantly blue and white colour scheme against a white background.\",\"0T9uPw\":\"Doc\",\"MRuvYA\":\"Add logos to be instantly recognisable\",\"mRySaw\":\"Continue\",\"6aVeZw\":\"一键“橘”祥写真\",\"fHtG5g\":\"Animation\",\"WOkpdA\":\"Sundanese\",\"D8ZpAQ\":\"Telugu\"}");
